rson%20at%20the%20Taiwan%20Affairs%20Office%2C%20at%20a%20regular%20news%20conference.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20northwest%20China%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20magnitude-6.2%20earthquake%20that%20destroyed%20over%20200%2C000%20homes%20and%20killed%20more%20than%20100%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-expresses-heartfelt-thanks-for-taiwan-earthquake-relief-assistance%2Farticleshow%2F106305844.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-expresses-heartfelt-thanks-for-taiwan-earthquake-relief-assistance%2Famp_articleshow%2F106305844.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-expresses-heartfelt-thanks-for-taiwan-earthquake-relief-assistance%2Famp_articleshow%2F106305844.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22War%20With%20Hamas%20Will%20Last%20For%20Months%2C%20Israel%20Warns%20Amid%20Fresh%20UN%20Alarm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20warned%20that%20its%20war%20with%20Hamas%20will%20last%20for%20months%20amid%20an%20United%20Nations%20alarm%20over%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20killing%20over%20100%20Palestinians%20in%20two%20days%20in%20the%20war-torn%20Gaza%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20shortcuts%20in%20dismantling%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20organisation%26quot%3B%2C%20Israel's%20military%20chief%20Herzi%20Halevi%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20war%20%26quot%3Bwill%20continue%20for%20many%20more%20months%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20magic%20solutions%2C%20there%20are%20no%20shortcuts%20in%20dismantling%20a%20terrorist%20organization%2C%20only%20determined%20and%20persistent%20fighting.%20We%20will%20reach%20Hamas%20leadership%20too%2C%20whether%20it%20takes%20a%20week%20or%20if%20it%20takes%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Halevi.%3C%2Fp%