2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26172822%2FMay-13_Naeem_Book-Launch_0002-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26172822%2FMay-13_Naeem_Book-Launch_0002-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690779%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBook%20launch%20at%20Pathshala%2C%20Dhaka.%20Photo%20by%20Shadman%20Sakib.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAmong%20essays%20covering%20art%20and%20culture%2C%20several%20explore%20issues%20emerging%20in%20the%20Bangladeshi%20art%20scene%2C%20like%20%E2%80%9CCheragee%20Pahar%3A%20Far%20From%20the%20Madding%20Crowd%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CDhali%20Al%20Mamoon%3A%20Unfolding%20Themselves%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CChobi%20Mela%3A%20What%20Was%20Chobi%20Mela%20and%20What%20Comes%20Next%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CDepart%3A%20Magazines%20in%20the%20(Empty)%20Forest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOthers%20capture%20prominent%20artists%20and%20their%20work%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CTareque%20Masud%3A%20On%20Adam%20Surat%20and%20Sultan.%E2%80%9D%20The%20book%20cover%20features%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20late%20filmmakers%20Tareque%20Masud%20and%20Mishuk%20Munier%2C%20who%20produced%20work%20mostly%20of%20the%20alternative%20genre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20also%20interviews%20with%20personalities%20like%20architect%20Salahuddin%20Ahmed%2C%20artist%20and%20teacher%20Dhali%20Al%20Mamoon%2C%20and%20Tayeba%20Begum%20Lipi%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20the%20Britto%20Artist%20Collective.%20These%20are%20invaluable%20for%20portraying%20the%20thinking%20of%20these%20luminaries%20around%20topics%20during%20a%20particular%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiterary%20figures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlso%20included%20are%20Mohaiemen%E2%80%99s%20commentaries%20on%20well-known%20international%20literary%20figures%20such%20as%20Taslima%20Nasreen%20and%20Zia%20Haider%20Rahman.%20One%20is%20in%20exile%20(an%20unproductive%20period%2C%20as%20the%20essay%20suggests)%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20formed%20by%20British%20diaspora%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThese%20essays%20capture%20the%20historical%20development%20of%20the%20art%20scene%20in%20the%20country%20and%20may%20provide%20impetus%20to%20future%20researchers%2C%20with%20materials%20like%20the%20graphic%20chronology%20of%20a%20photography%20biennial%20on%20pages%20138-145.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMohaiemen%20shows%20how%20to%20create%20space%20and%20to%20tease%20out%20the%20noise%20from%20real%20issues.%20In%20%E2%80%9CDocumentary%3A%20Social%20Realism%E2%80%99s%20Quest%20for%20Reality%E2%80%9D%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20offers%20a%20brief%20history%20of%20the%20development%20of%20photojournalism%20in%20recent%20decades.%20Critically%20examining%20the%20wider%20demand-elements%20in%20developing%20countries%2C%20he%20reveals%20the%20disappointing%20truth%20of%20continued%20dependence%20on%20Western%20countries%20for%20financial%20and%20technical%20aid%20as%20well%20as%20for%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFactors%20include%20a%20lack%20of%20maturity%20in%20building%20institutions%20and%20relatively%20slow%20progress%20in%20social%20acceptance%20around%20emerging%20issues%20like%20gender%20equality%20or%20same-sex%20love.%20He%20explores%20how%20images%20and%20their%20use%20in%20the%20developed%20world%20still%20fail%20to%20portray%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fremembering-painter-and-poet-imroz%5C%22%3ERemembering%20the%20Magic%20of%20Painter%20and%20Poet%20Imroz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20author%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20Bengali%20phrases%20to%20highlight%20issues%20and%20to%20offer%20remedies%20over%20a%20fairly%20long%20period%20underlines%20how%20scholars%20who%20leave%20their%20countries%20never%20stop%20yearning%20for%20their%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20book%20worth%20a%20reader%E2%80%99s%20time%20and%20money%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20well%20organised%2C%20with%20events%20and%20incidents%20aptly%20tagged%20to%20categories.%20It%20has%20been%20very%20carefully%20anthologised%2C%20with%20each%20piece%20stitching%20a%20narrative%20that%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20produces%20a%20much%20bigger%20story%20of%20the%20time.%20The%20table%20of%20contents%20alone%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20great%20archive%20of%20situations%20and%20historical%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConflicting%20voices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20puts%20a%20number%20of%20quality%20pieces%20in%20one%20place%2C%20some%20of%20which%20one%20may%20have%20missed%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20only%20downside%20is%20the%20printing%20quality.%20The%20current%20edition%2C%20black%20and%20white%2C%20uses%20paper%20that%20lowers%20the%20visual%20impact%20of%20some%20superbly%20curated%20photos.%20A%20niche%20market%20may%20be%20happy%20to%20absorb%20a%20slightly%20higher%20cost%20for%20better%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThose%20putting%20together%20the%20next%20edition%20might%20consider%20publishing%20the%20book%20or%20parts%20of%20it%20on%20better-quality%20paper.%20Another%20option%20wo