%20patches%20on%20the%20pitch%2C%20which%20had%20been%20covered%20since%20Sunday%20while%20a%20reported%2051mm%20of%20rain%20fell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wicket%20has%20been%20undercover%20for%20the%20past%20two%20days%20and%20there%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20moisture%20in%20the%20wicket%2C%20so%20we%20would%20like%20to%20make%20use%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20South%20African%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Temba%20Bavuma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1540-temba-bavuma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETemba%20Bavuma%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20opted%20for%20an%20all-seam%20attack%20and%20included%20two%20debutants%20in%20batsman%20David%20Bedingham%20and%20left-arm%20fast%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nandre%20Burger%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113424-nandre-burger-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENandre%20Burger%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20AFP%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703643660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5i4i7leo_ravi-shastri-bcci_625x300_17_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwould-have-beaten-south-africa-but-for-this-fellow-ravi-shastris-blockbuster-verdict-4745417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravi%20Shastri%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20has%20the%20perfect%20chance%20to%20win%20their%20first%20Test%20series%20ever%20on%20South%20African%20soil%20because%20of%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20single%20cricketer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwould-have-beaten-south-africa-but-for-this-fellow-ravi-shastris-blockbuster-verdict-4745417%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwould-have-beaten-south-africa-but-for-this-fellow-ravi-shastris-blockbuster-verdict-4745417%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwould-have-beaten-south-africa-but-for-this-fellow-ravi-shastris-blockbuster-verdict-4745417%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMost%20Fliers%20Had%20Return%20Tickets%26quot%3B%3A%20Lawyer%20Of%20Airline%20In%20'Donkey%20Flight'%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20of%20the%20airline%20whose%20plane%20was%20allegedly%20used%20for%20a%20'donkey%20flight'%20and%20was%20grounded%20in%20France%20has%20claimed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20passengers%20had%20hotel%20reservations%20and%20return%20tickets%20from%20Nicaragua%2C%20which%20was%20the%20destination%20as%20far%20as%20the%20company%20was%20concerned.%20Officials%20have%20said%20299%20of%20the%20plane's%20303%20passengers%20were%20Indian%20and%20the%20plane%20was%20grounded%20after%20a%20tip-off%20that%20the%20fliers%20were%20likely%20to%20be%20victims%20of%20human%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP%20that%20the%20plane%20may%20be%20linked%20to%20a%20crime%20syndicate%20attempting%20to%20smuggle%20individuals%20into%20the%20United%20States.%20Nicaragua%2C%20a%20central%20American%20nation%2C%20has%20seen%20a%20marked%20rise%20in%20Indians%20attempting%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Liliana%20Bakayoko%2C%20the%20lawyer%20for%20Romania-based%20Legend%20Airlines%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20lawyer%20of%20the%20company.%20My%20colleagues%20who%20defended%20the%20passengers%20before%20the%20judge%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20passengers%20they%20defended%20all%20had%20return%20tickets.%20They%20had%20hotel%20reservations%20and%20return%20tickets...%20I%20don't%20know%20for%20when%2C%20actually.%20But%20not%20for%20the%20next%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%20to%20her%20that%2C%20according%20to%20available%20information%2C%20only%2012%20of%20the%20303%20passengers%20had%20a%20return%20ticket%2C%20Ms%20Bakayoko%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20company's%20aeroplane%20was%20hired%20by%20a%20client%2C%20which%20is%20a%20foreign%20company%2C%20to%20perform%20such%20flights.%20According%20to%20my%20colleagues%20in%20France%2C%20all%20the%20passengers%20they%20defended%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20had%20return%20tickets%20and%20hotel%20reservations.%20But%20it%20is%20true%20that%20only%20three%20passengers%20were%20heard%20by%20the%20judge%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Peculiar%20Situation'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20after%20the%20plane%20landed%20in%20France's%20Vatry%20for%20refuelling%20on%20Friday%2C%20Ms%20Bakayoko%20said%20it%20was%20a%20peculiar%20situation%20because%20the%20airline's%20crew%20was%20ordered%20to%20leave%20the%20airport%2C%20go%20to%20a%20hotel%20and%20wait%20to%20be%20called%20to%20testify%20as%20witnesses.%20This%2C%20she%20said%2C%20meant%20leaving%20the%20passengers%20behind%20and%20the%20flight's%20Captain%20was%20wondering%20what%20to%20do%20because%20he%20had%20a%20duty%20towards%20the%20people%20in%20the%20plane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20crew%20was%20called%20two%20hours%20later%20and%20they%20were%20really%20afraid%20because%20they%20did%20not%20know%20exactly%20what%20was%20going%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20advised%20them%20to%20go%20and%20to%20say%20everything%20they%20know.%20So%20everybody%20went%20there%20and%20the%20interrogations%20took%20place.%20It%20took%20hours%20and%20they%20were%20all%20left%20free%20to%20go.%20But%20the%20plane%20was%20seized%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20expect.%20The%20passengers%20were%20all%20asked%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20airport.%20Later%20the%20plane%20was%20released%2C%20but%20the%20passengers%20were%20still%20retained.%20We%20decided%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20what%20happened%20with%20the%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHearings%20At%20Airport%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bakayoko%20said%20hearings%20were%20conducted%20at%20the%20airport.%20Judges%20went%20there%20with%20attorneys%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20passengers%20and%2C%20after%20three%20hearings%2C%20the%20judges%20declared%20that%20the%20procedure%20was%20irregular.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20French%20law%2C%20when%20the%20police%20detain%20somebody%2C%20they%20are%20obliged%20to%20notify%20the%20person%20their%20rights%2C%20with%20a%20translator%20if%20they%20don't%20speak%20French%2C%20and%20with%20an%20attorney.%20And%20there%20were%20no%20translators%20available%2C%20there%20were%20two%20translators%20and%20one%20of%20them%20left%20because%20of%20some%20personal%20considerations.%20So%20there%20were%20no%20available%20translators%2C%20and%20it%20took%20too%20long%20for%20the%20local%20authority%20to%20notify%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20judge%20said%20that%20the%20procedure%20is%20irregular%20because%20of%20this%2C%20because%20people%20have%20stayed%20within%20the%20airport%2C%20actually%20for%20hours%2C%20some%20for%2011%20hours%2C%20without%20knowing%20at%20all%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20without%20understanding%20the%20explanations.%20And%20nobody%20was%20giving%20explanations%2C%20actually%2C%20even%20in%20French.%20These%20people%20were%20afraid.%20So%20the%20judge%20ruled%20that%20the%20detention%20is%20irregular.%20The%20French%20authorities%20decided%20to%20let%20everybody%20go%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20said%20other%20problems%20arose%20because%20some%20of%20the%20passengers%20did%20not%20want%20to%20go%20to%20India%2C%20where%20the%20plane%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fplane-with-indians-held-in-france-for-days-lands-in-mumbai-4742915%5C%22%3Elanded%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20was%20the%20country%20that%20was%20ready%20to%20just%20accept%20the%20passengers%20very%20quickly.%20The%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20refused.%20Nicaragua%2C%20as%20far%20as%20we%20know%2C%20also%20(refused).%20So%2C%20as%20the%20passengers%20were%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20worked%20hard%20with%20the%20French%20authorities%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20process%20of%20obtaining%20all%20the%20permits%20necessary%20to%20fly%20to%20India.%20Some%20of%20them%20refused%20to%20go...%20In%20the%20end%2C%20276%20passengers%20boarded%20and%20left%20for%20India%20and%20the%20others%20requested%20asylum%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Was%20The%20Client%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bakayoko%20said%20the%20client%20who%20chartered%20the%20flight%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Nicaragua%20was%20responsible%20for%20checking%20the%20passengers'%20passports%2C%20tickets%20and%20visas.%20%C2%A0She%20said%20the%20client%20was%20a%20foreign%20company%2C%20a%20non-European%20one%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20disclose%20the%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressed%20on%20whether%20other%20flights%20to%20Nicaragua%20had%20been%20chartered%20by%20the%20same%20client%2C%20she%20answered%20in%20the%20affirmative%2C%20but%20said%20she%20did%20not%20have%20the%20data%20on%20hand%20to%20say%20how%20many%20Indians%20were%20aboard%20such%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Donkey%20flights'%20refer%20to%20a%20method%20used%20by%20some%20migrants%20wherein%20they%20transit%20through%20third%20countries%20with%20lenient%20travel%20document%20requirements%20to%20reach%20their%20final%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703642760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fb5ee70sg_mumbai-passengers-france_625x300_27_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fi