%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Apple%20released%20its%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%209%2C%20touting%20increased%20performance%20along%20with%20features%20such%20as%20the%20ability%20to%20access%20and%20log%20health%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20disagree%20with%20the%20USITC%20decision%20and%20resulting%20exclusion%20order%2C%20and%20are%20taking%20all%20measures%20to%20return%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%209%20and%20Apple%20Watch%20Ultra%202%20to%20customers%20in%20the%20US%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Apple%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20original%20decision%2C%20Apple%20said%20Masimo%20had%20%26quot%3Bwrongly%20attempted%20to%20use%20the%20ITC%20to%20keep%20a%20potentially%20lifesaving%20product%20from%20millions%20of%20US%20consumers%20while%20making%20way%20for%20their%20own%20watch%20that%20copies%20Apple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20trial%20of%20Masimo's%20allegations%20ended%20in%20a%20mistrial%20after%20jurors%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20unanimous%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20year%2C%20Apple%20filed%20two%20patent%20infringement%20lawsuits%20accusing%20Masimo%20of%20copying%20Apple%20Watch%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Masimo%20was%20cleared%20by%20US%20regulators%20to%20use%20its%20own%20wrist-worn%20product%20for%20prescription%20and%20over-the-counter%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20company%20is%20using%20litigation%20to%20make%20way%20for%20its%20own%20Apple%20Watch-inspired%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703642160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Frlqf7btg_apple-watch-sensor-can-accurately-predict-stress-levels-of-users_625x300_01_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http