0Toledo%20Ohio.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c81197a3c8094d5dd8694%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22890%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20a%20few%20dates%20with%20someone%20new%2C%20you%20may%20notice%20certain%20signs%20that%20they're%20into%20you%2C%20therapist%20Alfonso%20Ferguson%20said.%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Noritz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20you're%20dating%20someone%20new%2C%20you%20probably%20want%20to%20know%20if%20they%20like%20you%20as%20much%20as%20you%20like%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20a%20few%20dates%2C%20you%20should%20trust%20your%20gut%20and%20look%20for%20promising%20patterns%2C%20a%20therapist%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThings%20like%20check-in%20rituals%20and%20insightful%20questions%20could%20signal%20mutual%20interest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20ever%20crushed%20hard%20on%20a%20new%20love%20interest%2C%20you%20may%20have%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20analyze%20their%20every%20action%20and%20decipher%20their%20words%20for%20hidden%20meaning%20as%20you%20try%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20they%20like%20you%20back%20just%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20everyone%20shows%20their%20romantic%20interest%20in%20different%20ways.%20Some%20prefer%20to%20be%20forthright%20about%20their%20budding%20feelings%2C%20but%20others%20can%20feel%20too%20anxious%20to%20say%20how%20they%20feel%2C%20primarily%20using%20their%20actions%20to%20express%20interest%20instead%2C%20according%20to%20therapist%20Alfonso%20Ferguson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20you%20shouldn't%20read%20into%20interactions%20with%20your%20new%20partner%20too%20much.%26quot%3BTrust%20your%20gut%20as%20much%20as%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Ferguson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20still%20feeling%20uncertain%20%E2%80%94%20because%20you%20haven't%20felt%20this%20way%20before%2C%20or%20have%20major%20brainworms%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fred-flag-meme-meaning-facebook-twitter-tiktok-warning-signs-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3Bred%20flag%26quot%3B%20relationship%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20TikTok%20videos%20%E2%80%94%20Ferguson%20said%20there%20are%20a%20few%20signs%20you%20can%20look%20out%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20aren't%20things%20that%20you'll%20see%20on%20a%20very%20first%20date%2C%20or%20in%20the%20first%20encounter%2C%26quot%3B%20Ferguson%20said.%20But%20if%20you%20notice%20this%20person%20consistently%20does%20these%20things%2C%20it%20means%20your%20relationship%20is%20mutual%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20initiate%20plans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20love%20interest%20is%20really%20into%20you%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20want%20to%20see%20you%20again%2C%20and%20will%20make%20that%20known%2C%20according%20to%20Ferguson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20look%20like%20them%20asking%20for%20another%20date%20while%20you're%20currently%20on%20one%2C%20or%20reaching%20out%20over%20text%20or%20the%20phone%20soon%20after%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20what's%20your%20schedule%20like%20next%20week%3F%20I%20want%20to%20see%20you%20again%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Ferguson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20initiating%20plans%20could%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20intention%2C%20something%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmake-relationship-happier-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebuilds%20intimacy%20and%20trust%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20couple%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20relationship%20stage%20they're%20currently%20in%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20fit%20you%20into%20their%20schedule%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20they're%20busy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20new%20boo%20isn't%20reaching%20out%20to%20make%20plans%2C%20it%20might%20seem%20like%20they%20don't%20like%20you%20as%20much%20as%20you%20like%20them.%20But%20don't%20assume%20that%2C%20Ferguson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20for%20some%20folks%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fanxious-attachment-style%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanxiety%20of%20being%20rejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20cause%20them%20to%20avoid%20reaching%20out%20first%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20a%20romance.%20And%20for%20people%20in%20same-sex%20relationships%2C%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20determine%20expectations%20about%20who%20does%20the%20asking%20out%20when%20you're%20just%20starting%20to%20know%20them%2C%20Ferguson%20told%20BI.%20(He%20regularly%20counsels%20LGBTQ%2B%20clients%2C%20who%20say%20straight%2C%20opposite-gender%20dating%20norms%20can%20make%20this%20situation%20feel%20even%20more%20confusing%20to%20navigate.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20luckily%2C%20there's%20another%20simple%20way%20to%20gauge%20your%20lover's%20interest%20in%20you%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20involves%20a%20little%20bravery%20on%20your%20part.%20If%20you%20express%20interest%20in%20connecting%20first%2C%20either%20in-person%20or%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20they%20find%20a%20way%20to%20make%20it%20work%2C%20according%20to%20Ferguson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20someone's%20life%20is%20already%20full%20of%20work%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20family%20responsibilities%2C%20they'll%20create%20space%20for%20you%20if%20they%20want%20to%20build%20a%20connection%2C%20Ferguson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20a%20check-in%20ritual%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you've%20been%20on%20a%20few%20dates%2C%20getting%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsix-second-kiss-better-marriage-relationship-advice-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-key%20ritual%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20your%20lover%20could%20be%20another%20sign%20of%20a%20promising%20connection%2C%20said%20Ferguson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20and%20your%20honey%20get%20into%20the%20routine%20of%20sending%20each%20other%20good%20morning%20or%20good%20night%20texts%2C%20scheduling%20weekly%20FaceTime%20calls%2C%20or%20passing%20silly%20memes%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20it's%20a%20sign%20they're%20invested%20in%20your%20relationship%2C%20according%20to%20Ferguson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20consistent%20check-ins%2C%20even%20brief%20text-%20or%20picture-based%20ones%2C%20show%20they're%20thinking%20about%20you%20and%20are%20available%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20ask%20you%20insightful%20questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20wants%20to%20take%20their%20connection%20with%20you%20to%20a%20deeper%20level%2C%20they'll%20also%20make%20it%20a%20point%20to%20ask%20about%20things%20like%20your%20tastes%2C%20opinions%2C%20and%20important%20relationships%2C%20according%20to%20Ferguson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20should%20go%20beyond%2C%20'What%20are%20you%20doing%3F'%20It's%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fquestions-to-ask-people%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrying%20to%20get%20to%20know%20you%20better%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-signs-he-she-they-like-you-therapist-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703637301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c818b0ec98e92f74ffb70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-signs-he-she-they-like-you-therapist-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20few%20signs%20that%20the%20person%20you're%20dating%20likes%20you%20include%20making%20time%20for%20you%2C%20initiating%20plans%2C%20and%20asking%20deeper%20questions%2C%20a%20therapist%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnaftulin%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Naftulin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A