r%20a%20nation-state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELarge-scale%20vs.%20small-scale%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20how%20the%20film%20suggests%20that%20cellphone%20service%20was%20disrupted%20across%20all%20networks%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20have%20been%20cases%20when%20cell%20networks%20have%20been%20shut%20down%2C%20Heitzenrater%20said%20that%20taking%20down%20the%20entire%20network%20of%20just%20one%20provider%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fverizon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVerizon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20owns%20its%20telecommunications%20network%2C%20%26quot%3Bwould%20be%20hard%20to%20imagine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20could%20be%20some%20aspect%20of%20a%20provider%20in%20which%20a%20bad%20actor%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20vulnerability%20that%20can%20impact%20its%20entire%20network%20%E2%80%94%20in%20his%20field%20of%20work%2C%20Heitzenrater%20says%20he's%20not%20one%20to%20say%20anything%20is%20impossible%20%E2%80%94%20but%20a%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20likely%26quot%3B%20scenario%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20regional%20or%20limited%26quot%3B%20impact%20on%20one%20cellphone%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20goes%20for%20the%20widespread%20impact%20of%20transportation.%20In%20the%20film%2C%20the%20navigation%20systems%20of%20ships%2C%20airplanes%2C%20and%20Teslas%20are%20somehow%20overridden.%20A%20more%20plausible%20plan%20would%20be%20a%20localized%20impact%20on%20planes%20since%20air%20travel%20is%20increasingly%20automated%2C%20Heitzenrater%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJasson%20Casey%2C%20CEO%20of%20Beyond%20Identity%2C%20an%20authentication%20platform%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsletters%2F2023-12-20%2Fleave-the-world-behind-could-netflix-movie-s-cyberattack-actually-happen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20hacking%20boats%20and%20planes%20and%20sending%20%26quot%3Bfake%20navigation%20signals%26quot%3B%20is%20possible%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20the%20planes%20and%20boats%20still%20have%20an%20ability%20for%20the%20crew%20to%20take%20over%20if%20something%20seems%20amiss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20even%20think%20this%20would%20be%20likely%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitzenrater%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20more%20concerning%20scenario%20would%20be%20if%20someone%20were%20to%20disrupt%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration's%20computerized%20planning%20systems%2C%20in%20which%20case%20flights%20would%20have%20to%20stay%20grounded%20until%20the%20problem%20is%20solved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20cyberwarfare%20cheap%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20a%20cyberattack%20of%20this%20level%20is%20%26quot%3Bcost-effective%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20hard%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20answer%20that%20question%2C%20I%20would%20have%20one%20of%20those%20papers%20that%20everybody%20references%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitzenrater%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20operation%20of%20this%20scale%20certainly%20wouldn't%20be%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20can%20make%20a%20cyberattack%20%26quot%3Bcheap%26quot%3B%20is%20that%20vulnerabilities%20in%20a%20particular%20system%20can%20sometimes%20allow%20hackers%20to%20impact%20a%20lot%20of%20targets%2C%20and%20the%20bad%20actor%20can%20use%20that%20vulnerability%20repeatedly%2C%20he%20said.%20And%20in%20the%20case%20of%20one%20cybercriminal%20taking%20advantage%20of%20some%20vulnerability%20through%2C%20for%20example%2C%20ransomware%2C%20the%20operation%20would%20be%20fairly%20inexpensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20a%20larger%20scale%2C%20finding%20vulnerabilities%20across%20multiple%20sectors%20would%20require%20immense%20reconnaissance%20or%20intelligence%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20think%20about%20it%20in%20that%20aggregate%2C%20then%20it's%20not%20as%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitzenrater%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-leave-the-world-behind-movie-cyberattack-real-life-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703631985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658b4cf41c5c7b8c9a0c20cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-leave-the-world-behind-movie-cyberattack-real-life-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Netflix's%20new%20movie%2C%20%26quot%3BLeave%20the%20World%20Behind%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20cyberattack%20shuts%20down%20communications%20across%20the%20US.%20Experts%20say%20it's%20unlikely%20in%20real%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-leave-the-world-behind-movie-cyberattack-real-life-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MBA%20grad%20held%20for%20offensive%20posts%20against%20Pawar%2C%20Uddhav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703631419000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106304101%2Cimgsize-21050.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmba-grad-held-for-offensive-posts-against-pawar-uddhav%2Farticleshow%2F106304091.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2033-year-old%20MBA%20degree-holder%2C%20Vishal%20Gorde%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBD-Belapur%20police%20for%20posting%20defamatory%20comments%20on%20social%20media%20against%20NCP%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20NCP%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20ex-CM%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20NCP%20MLA%20Rohit%20Pawar%2C%20and%20UBT%20Sena%20MLA%20Aaditya%20Thackeray.%20Gorde%20deliberately%20made%20objectionable%20comments%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20to%20create%20animosity%20and%20riots%2C%20according%20to%20a%20complaint.%20He%20was%20ar