0medication%20lost%2020%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20an%20average%20of%2052%20pounds%2C%20in%20in%20about%2016-months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmounjaro-for-weight-loss-trial-participants-lost-15-of-bodyweight-2023-6%5C%22%3E%20clinical%20trial%20%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20nearly%20half%20of%20overweight%2C%20diabetic%20patients%20taking%20the%20drug%20lost%20at%20least%2015%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Blandmark%26quot%3B%20result%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study's%20lead%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20study%20also%20found%20that%20people%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzepbound-weight-gain-stop-taking-tirzepatide-2023-12%5C%22%3Estop%20taking%20tirzepatide%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20regain%20at%20least%20some%20fo%20the%20weight%20they%20lost%20on%20the%20medication.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESide%20effects%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ETirzepatide%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmounjaro-vs-ozempic-side-effects-2023-5%3Finline-endstory-related-recommendations%3D%5C%22%3Esimilar%20side%20effects%20as%20semaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20gastrointestinal%20issues%2C%20but%20they%20may%20be%20less%20severe%2C%20mitigated%20by%20the%20drug's%20effect%20on%20both%20hormones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20you've%20heard%20of%20it%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELike%C2%A0semaglutide%2C%20tirzepatide%20has%20made%20a%20name%20for%20itself%20in%20the%20media%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmounjaro-cost-without-coupon-regain-weight-loss-drug-2023-5%5C%22%3Edramatic%20weight-loss%20stories%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20social%20media%20trends%2C%20as%20well%20as%20concerns%20from%20patients%20about%20accessing%20the%20drug%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%241%2C023%20per%20month%20for%20Mounjaro%2C%20%241%2C059.87%20for%20Zepbound%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiraglutide%20(sold%20as%20Victroza%20and%20Saxenda)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Liraglutide%2C%20also%20sold%20by%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20has%20been%20available%20the%20longer%20than%20comparable%20GLP-1%20medications%2C%20approved%20in%202010%20for%20diabetes%20and%20in%202014%20for%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20is%C2%A0less%20long-lasting%20than%20newer%20drugs%2C%20and%20therefore%20needs%20to%20be%20adminsitered%20as%20a%20once-daily%20injection%20instead%20of%20once-weekly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEffectiveness%20in%20clinical%20trials%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EResearch%20suggests%20patients%20lost%20about%205%20to%2010%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20according%20to%20one%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5358074%2F%3Freport%3Dclassic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESide%20effects%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20liraglutide%20has%20similar%20gastrointestinal%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8017323%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20other%20GLP-1%20drugs%2C%20it's%20also%20been%20linked%20to%20more%20concerning%20reactions%2C%20such%20as%20pancreatitis%2C%20gallbladder%20disease%20and%20in%20rare%20cases%2C%20mental%20health%20symptoms%20such%20as%20worsening%20depression%20or%20insomnia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAbout%20%241%2C349%20per%20month%20for%20Saxenda%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetatrutide%3A%20the%20newest%20medication%20pending%20FDA%20approval%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnew-weight-loss-and-diabetes-drug-retatrutide-awaits-further-testing-2022-12%5C%22%3ERetatrutide%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20newest%20contender%20in%20once-weekly%20injectable%20GLP-1%20medications%2C%20currently%20slated%20for%20phase%203%20trials%2C%20from%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Eli%20Lilly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20earned%20the%20nickname%20%26quot%3Btriple%20G%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20works%20on%20three%20different%20hormonal%20pathways.%20Similarly%20to%20semaglutide%2C%20reatrutide%20acts%20on%20GLP-1%2C%20and%20like%20tirzepatide%2C%20it%20acts%20on%20GIP.%C2%A0However%2C%20it%20adds%20yet%20another%20interaction%20to%20the%20mix%20by%20targeting%20receptors%20for%20another%20hormone%20called%20glucagon%2C%20which%20influences%20blood%20sugar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEffectiveness%20in%20clinical%20trials%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fretatrutide-patients-lose-more-weight-than-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-2023-6%5C%22%3Emost%20recent%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20June%2026%20in%20The%20New%20England%20Journal%20of%20Medicine%2C%20showed%20that%20patients%20taking%20the%20highest%20dose%20of%20the%20medication%20once%20a%20week%20lost%2024.2%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20in%2048%20weeks%2C%20results%20comparable%20to%20those%20seen%20with%20bariatric%20surgery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESide%20effects%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EResearch%20is%20still%20underway%20to%20understand%20possible%20side%20effects%20of%20retatrutide.%20Available%20evidence%20suggests%20any%20issues%20are%20mostly%20gastrointestinal%2C%20and%20can%20be%20managed%20by%20starting%20with%20a%20lower%20dose%20and%20gradually%20increasing%2C%20similar%20to%20other%20GLP-1%20drugs.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETBD%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-weight-loss-meds-injections-compare-costs-results-side-effects%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publis