Shaitan%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20black-and-white%20war%20films%20ever%20made%2C%20and%20remembered%20for%20the%20song%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAb%20tumhare%20hawale%20watan%20saathyion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FkvSeGR-qcz0%3Fsi%3DtZlkdvEnss_jVBNR%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dismantling%20of%20the%20site%20was%20undertaken%20in%20February%202021%2C%20after%20India%20and%20China%20announced%20disengagement%20at%20Pangong%20Tso%2C%20when%20a%20buffer%20zone%20was%20created%20on%20the%20north%20bank%20of%20the%20lake%20and%20to%20its%20south.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20had%20announced%20the%20disengagement%20between%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20February%2011%2C%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20details%20about%20the%20disengagement%20process%20or%20buffer%20zones%20have%20been%20shared%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20with%20the%20nation%20so%20far.%20The%20news%20of%20the%20landmark%20being%20dismantled%20was%20revealed%20for%20the%20first%20time%20by%20the%20elected%20councillor%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20defence%20ministry%20and%20the%20army%20have%20not%20refuted%20the%20councillor%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERezang%20La%20in%20Chushul%20sector%20saw%20a%20gallant%20battle%20fought%20till%20the%20%E2%80%9Clast%20man%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Clast%20round%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20company%20of%20the%2013%20Kumaon%20battalion%2C%20which%20was%20led%20by%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20all%20odds%20and%20grossly%20outnumbered%2C%20the%20valiant%20soldiers%20repulsed%20seven%20attacks%20by%20the%20Chinese%2C%20launched%20in%20waves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20heavy%20artillery%20shelling%20and%20fierce%20Chinese%20assaults%2C%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%20and%20his%20113%20bravehearts%20delivered%20the%20heaviest%20blow%20to%20the%20Chinese.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallantryawards.gov.in%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2Fhome_banner%2FBatleofrezangLa-2023-11-18.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefence%20ministry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20several%20hours%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20battle%20hung%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20balance.%20Men%20were%20engaged%20in%20hand-to-hand%20combat.%20The%20Indian%20Company%20Commander%20even%20tried%20to%20launch%20a%20platoon%20counterattack%20to%20regain%20the%20height%2C%20Point%205300%20but%20did%20not%20succeed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20telephone%20line%20to%20the%20Battalion%20HQ%20was%20cut%20and%20the%20company%20radio%20set%20was%20destroyed%20in%20the%20initial%20stages.%20C%20Company%2013%20KUMAON%20was%20now%20on%20its%20own.%20No%20reinforcements%20could%20reach%20them.%20For%20them%20it%20was%20a%20fight%20to%20the%20finish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20valour%20of%20the%20Charlie%20Company%20not%20only%20successfully%20stopped%20China%E2%80%99s%20advance%2C%20but%20it%20also%20resulted%20in%20the%20Chushul%20airport%20being%20saved%2C%20thereby%20preventing%20a%20possible%20Chinese%20occupation%20of%20the%20entire%20Ladakh%20region%20in%201962.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeneral%20K.S.%20Thimayya%20was%20to%20state%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20rarely%20come%20across%20such%20%5Ban%5D%20example%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20world%20military%20history%20when%20braving%20such%20heavy%20odds%2C%20the%20men%20fought%20till%20the%20last%20bullet%20and%20the%20last%20man.%20Certainly%20the%20Battle%20of%20Rezang%20La%20is%20such%20a%20shining%20example.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20at%20Rezang%20La%2C%20114%20soldiers%20perished%20in%20the%20fighting%20while%20five%20were%20captured%20by%20the%20Chinese.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20posthumously%20awarded%20the%20Param%20Vir%20Chakra%20while%20another%20nine%20gallantry%20awards%20were%20won%20by%20the%20sub-unit%2C%20including%20five%20Vir%20Chakras%20and%20four%20Sena%20Medals.%20Singh%20was%20the%20second%20winner%20of%20the%20Param%20Vir%20Chakra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20Company%20was%20re-raised%20and%20rechristened%20as%20%E2%80%98Rezang%20La%20Company%E2%80%99%20in%201963.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallantryawards.gov.in%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2Fstyles%2Fawardee_img%2Fpublic%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FVrC_Jem_RamChander_221202_SS_compressed-2023-03-23-1212-0303.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHonorary%20captain%20Ram%20Chander%20Yadav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Havaldar%20Nihal%20Singh%2C%20two%20of%20the%20survivors%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-archive%2Fweb%2Fnobody-believed-we-had-killed-so-many-chinese-at-rezang-la-our-commander-called-me-crazy-and-warned-that-i-could-be-courtmartialled%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espoke%20about%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20fiftieth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20battle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703617147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F27001849%2F4va.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frezang-la-battle-landmark-removed-as-part-of-disengagement-councillor-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Haqeeqat%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20Hindi%20film%20released%20in%201964%20to%20national%20acclaim%2C%20was%20constructed%20around%20the%20battle%20of%20Rezang%20La%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20showcased%20a%20fictionalised%20version%20of%20the%20last%20stand%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20Company%2C%2013%20Kumaon%20led%20by%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh.%20Singh%20was%20posthumously%20awarded%20the%20Param%20Vir%20Chakra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frezang-la-battle-landmark-removed-as-part-of-disengagement-councillor-says%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20Orders%20Himachal%20To%20Shift%20Top%20Cop%20Over%20Extortion%20Complaint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20shift%20the%20state%20police%20chief%20and%20the%20Kangra%20superintendent%20of%20police%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20influence%20the%20investigation%20into%20a%20businessman's%20complaint%20about%20extortion%20and%20threat%20to%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20court%20also%20said%20it%20was%20intervening%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20circumstances%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20%26quot%3Bmore%20particularly%20when%20the%20respondent%20Home%20Secretary%20had%20chosen%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%26quot%3B%20to%20material%20presented%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%20filed%20on%20October%2028%2C%20Palampur-based%20businessman%20Nishant%20Sharma%20alleged%20threat%20to%20him%2C%20his%20family%20and%20property.%20He%20had%20also%20questioned%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Sanjay%20Kundu%2C%20who%20had%20allegedly%20made%20calls%20to%20him%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20come%20to%20Shimla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShift%20them%20(the%20DGP%20and%20the%20Kangra%20police%20chief)%20to%20other%20posts%20where%20they%20would%20not%20have%20any%20opportunity%20to%20influence%20the%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20MS%20Ramachandra%20Rao%20and%20Justice%20Jyotsna%20Rewal%20Dua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20light%20of%20the%20material%20available%20to%20us%20in%20this%20case%20till%20date%2C%20we%20are%20satisfied%20that%20exceptional%20circumstances%20do%20exist%20for%20intervening%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20more%20particularly%20when%20the%20respondent%20Home%20Secretary%20had%20chosen%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20said%20material%20for%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20Kangra%20SP%20showed%20very%20little%20progress%20in%20the%20investigation%20after%20having%20deliberately%20delayed%20the%20registration%20of%20FIR%20till%20November%2016%2C%20despite%20having%20received%20a%20complaint%20on%20October%2028%20through%20an%20email%20from%20the%20complainant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20November%2010%2C%20taking%20note%20of%20the%20businessman's%20complaint%2C%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20had%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20SPs%20of%20Shimla%20and%20Kangra%20to%20file%20a%20status%20report%20in%20the%20court%20regarding%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20also%20marked%20to%20the%20chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%2C%20businessman%20Sharma%20had%20alleged%20impending%20threat%20to%20him%2C%20his%20family%20members%20and%20property%20from%20his%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20an%20incident%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20him%20in%20Gurugram%20on%20August%2025%2C%20saying%20two%20influential%20persons%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20including%20a%20former%20IPS%20officer%2C%20were%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20Palampur%20in%20Kangra%20district%20after%20the%20attack%20but%20the%20DGP%20called%20me%20up%20from%20his%20official%20number%20and%20forced%20me%20to%20come%20to%20Shimla%20and%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day%20two%20criminals%2C%20stopped%20me%20at%20Mcleodganj%20in%20Dharamshala%20and%20threatened%20to%20harm%20my%20two-and-half-year%20old%20kid%20and%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20drove%20to%20the%20house%20of%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Kangra%20at%20Dharamshala%20and%20narrated%20the%20plight%20to%20her%20and%20gave%20her%20my%20complaint%20but%20nothing%20has%20been%20done%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20demand%20an%20independent%20and%20unbiased%20investigation%20and%20lodging%20of%20an%20FIR%20against%20everyone%2C%20including%20the%20DGP.%20This%20is%20the%20only%20way%20you%20would%20be%20able%20to%20apprehend%20this%20whole%20gang%20of%20extortionists%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20case%20of%20defamation%20was%20registered%20against%20Nishant%20Sharma%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20DGP%20for%20harming%20his%20reputation%20and%20attempting%20to%20malign%20his%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20DGP%20Sanjay%20Kundu%20said%20Sharma%20had%2C%20on%20October%2029%2C%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20DGP%20on%20his%20official%20email%2C%20marking%20copies%20to%20other%20officials%2C%20in%20which%20he%20made%20false%20allegations%20with%20intentions%20to%20harm%20his%20reputation%20and%20tarnish%20his%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20under%20sections%20211%20(false%20charge%20of%20offence%20made%20with%20intent%20to%20injure)%2C%20469%20(forgery%20for%20purpose%20of%20harming%20reputation)%2C%20499%20(defamation)%20and%20500%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20was%20registered%20against%20the%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff