%20not%20trying%20to%20save%20her%20life.%20Notably%2C%20the%20woman%20died%20after%20she%20consumed%20half%20a%20litre%20of%20strong%20alcohol%20at%20the%20dinner%20party%20with%20her%20three%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3246134%2Fheartbroken-chinese-woman-dies-after-marathon-boozing-session-friends-ordered-pay-compensation%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20May%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20woman%2C%20identified%20by%20the%20nickname%20Xiaoqiu%2C%20went%20to%20her%20friend%20Wang%20Qi's%20home%20for%20a%20dinner%20party%2C%20and%20they%20were%20joined%20by%20two%20other%20friends%20Xu%20and%20Chen.%20The%20purpose%20of%20the%20gathering%20was%20for%20the%20women%20to%20support%20Ms%20Xiaoqiu%20who%20was%20upset%20after%20her%20boyfriend%20broke%20up%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20party%2C%20Ms%20Xiaoqiu%20consumed%20a%20total%20of%20half%20a%20litre%20of%20Chinese%20baijiu%20liquor%2C%20known%20for%20its%20high%20alcohol%20content.%20Ms%20Wang%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20drank%200.25%20litre.%20The%20other%20two%20women%20did%20not%20drink%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20that%20Ms%20Xiaoqiu%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Ms%20Xu%2C%20went%20to%20her%20car%20to%20rest%20after%20dinner.%20However%2C%20Ms%20Xu%20fell%20asleep%20and%20when%20she%20woke%20at%20about%205%20am%20the%20next%20day%2C%20she%20realised%20her%20friend%20was%20not%20breathing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Xi%20immediately%20called%20an%20ambulance%20but%20doctors%20announced%20Ms%20Xiaoqiu's%20death%20an%20hour%20later.%20They%20said%20she%20had%20died%20of%20cardiorespiratory%20arrest%20caused%20by%20alcohol%20poisoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcheaper-than-living-on-land-us-couple-sells-everyt