k%20drone%20fired%20from%20Iran%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20track%20down%20those%20behind%20attacks%20on%20Merchant%20Navy%20ships%2C%20%26quot%3Beven%20from%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20sea%26quot%3B%20and%20take%20action%20against%20them%2C%20Union%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMV%20Chem%20Pluto%2C%20an%20oil%20tanker%2C%20had%20sailed%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20was%20headed%20for%20Mangaluru%20in%20Karnataka%20when%20it%20was%20attacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20oil%20tanker%20-%20the%20Gabon-registered%20MV%20Sai%20Baba%2C%20with%2025%20Indian%20crew%20members%20on%20board%20-%20was%20also%20attacked%20by%20a%20drone%20in%20the%20Southern%20Red%20Sea%2C%20Indian%20and%20American%20military%20officials%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703613480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Faodsptoo_drone-attack-on-ship_625x300_26_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplosives-detonated-fully-navy-finds-debris-of-drone-that-hit-ship-4747678%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20explosives%20that%20had%20struck%20merchant%20ship%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto%20had%20detonated%20fully%2C%20experts%20who%20examined%20the%20remains%20have%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplosives-detonated-fully-navy-finds-debris-of-drone-that-hit-ship-4747678%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplosives-detonated-fully-navy-finds-debris-of-drone-that-hit-ship-4747678%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplosives-detonated-fully-navy-finds-debris-of-drone-that-hit-ship-4747678%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Couple%20Sells%20'Everything'%20To%20Live%20On%20Cruise%20Ships%2C%20Claims%20It's%20Cheaper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20in%20the%20US%20who%20sold%20everything%20they%20owned%20three%20years%20ago%20to%20live%20their%20dream%20of%20sailing%20around%20the%20world%20say%20that%20is%20cheaper%20than%20living%20on%20land.%20John%20and%20Melody%20Hennessee%2C%20a%20couple%20from%20Florida%2C%20sold%20their%20home%2C%20business%2C%20and%20most%20of%20their%20belongings%20to%20embark%20on%20global%20travel%20in%202020%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F12%2F25%2Flifestyle%2Fthis-couple-sold-everything-to-live-on-cruise-ships%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20initially%20bought%20a%20motorhome%20to%20travel%20across%20the%20United%20States.%20However%2C%20when%20Mr%20Hennessee%20got%20tired%20of%20driving%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20to%20the%20seas.%20The%20couple%C2%A0saw%20a%20Facebook%20ad%20for%20a%20Royal%20Caribbean%20cruise%20that%20lasted%20274%20days%2C%20and%209%20months%20and%20jumped%20at%20the%20opportunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fmelody.fortier.7%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0uNjpKVxQsd7nkarV93Ks7AFNq4sCvmiAqVXtQsgvQXethKgW8HiHoKLbGAauHv6ol%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20quickly%20registered%20their%20names%20on%20the%20board%20and%20have%20since%20travelled%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20journeyed%20to%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20South%20Pacific%20and%20are%20presently%20navigating%20around%20the%20Dominican%20Republic.%20They%20say%20that%20it's%20cheaper%20than%20the%20landlocked%20life%20they%20led%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20now%20have%20a%20telephone%20bill%2C%20a%20shipping%20bill%2C%20and%20a%20few%20credit%20card%20bills%20for%20when%20we%20go%20ashore%2C%20but%20that's%20it.%20We%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20mortgage%20or%20the%20expense%20of%20homes.%20We%20no%20longer%20have%20vehicle%20insurance%2C%20property%20insurance%2C%20or%20utility%20bills.%20The%20list%20goes%20on.%20We%20are%20certain%20cruising%20is%20cheaper.%20Right%20now%20it%20is%20probably%20close%20to%20half%20of%20what%20it%20was%20when%20we%20lived%20on%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hennessee%C2%A0told%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-couple-who-sold-everything-to-live-on-cruise-ships-for-the-rest-of-their-lives-13028137%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20usually%20dock%20at%20their%20destination%20and%20explore%20for%20three%20to%20five%20days%20at%20a%20time.%C2%A0They%20are%20fully%20booked%20with%20trips%20until%20December%202024%20and%C2%A0will%20soon%20be%20boarding%20a%20residential%20cruise%20ship%C2%A0Villa%20Vie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Villa%20Vie%20Odyssey%20is%20an%20all-inclusive%20cruise%20ship%20providing%20permanent%20residences%2C%20with%20approximately%2030%25%20of%20passengers%20becoming%20full-time%20inhabitants.%20It%20will%20set%20off%20from%20Southampton%20in%20May%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20cabin%20so%20we%20can%20design%20it%20how%20we%20want.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20home%20for%20us%2C%20for%20probably%20a%20minimum%20of%2015%20years%20on%20the%20ship.%20We%20are%20just%20water%20people.%20We%20are%20both%20boaters.%20We%20love%20being%20on%20the%20ocean%2C''%C2%A0said%20Melody%20Hennessee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20the%20Hennessees%2C%20Angelyn%2C%20and%20Richard%20Burk%2C%20also%20from%20America%2C%20sold%20their%20home%20for%20a%20life%20at%20sea%20after%20a%20freak%20accident%20ten%20years%20ago.%C2%A0They%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%