2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0Also%20known%20as%20'zombie%20deer%20disease'%2C%C2%A0the%20illness%20that%20leaves%20animals%20confused%20and%20drooling%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-case-of-zombie-deer-disease-found-in-us-yellowstone-park-know-what-it-is-4589381%5C%22%3Efirst%20detected%20in%C2%A0Yellowstone%20National%20Park%20in%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20disease%20has%20been%20found%20in%20800%20samples%20of%20deer%2C%20elk%2C%20and%20moose%20across%20Wyoming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20labeled%20CWD%20as%20a%20''slow-moving%20disaster''%20and%20are%20strongly%20advising%20governments%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20likelihood%20of%20its%20transmission%20to%20humans.%20According%20to%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20the%20disease%20has%20been%20reported%20in%2031%20states%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20mad%20cow%20disease%20outbreak%20in%20Britain%20provided%20an%20example%20of%20how%2C%20overnight%2C%20things%20can%20get%20crazy%20when%20a%20spillover%20event%20happens%20from%2C%20say%2C%20livestock%20to%20people.%20We're%20talking%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20something%20similar%20occurring.%20No%20one%20is%20saying%20that%20it's%20going%20to%20happen%2C%20but%20people%20need%20to%20be%20prepared%2C''%C2%A0CWD%20researcher%20Dr%20Cory%20Anderson%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2023%2Fdec%2F22%2Fzombie-deer-disease-yellowstone-scientists-fears-fatal-chronic-wasting-disease-cwd-jump-species-barrier-humans-aoe%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20is%20worrying%20that%20there%20is%20no%20known%20way%20to%20eradicate%20it%2C%20''neither%20from%20the%20animals%20it%20infects%20nor%20the%20environment%20it%20contaminates.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20known%20case%20of%20CWD%20in%20humans%20has%20ever%20been%20recorded%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Fzombie-deer-disease-concerns-scientists-possible-spread-humans%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22URL%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Fzombie-deer-disease-concerns-scientists-possible-spread-humans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20studies%20have%20suggested%20chronic%20wasting%20disease%20is%20a%20risk%20to%20monkeys%20that%20eat%20infected%20animal%20meat%20or%20come%20in%20contact%20with%20infected%20animal%20brains%20or%20bodily%20fluids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''These%20studies%20raise%20concerns%20that%20there%20may%20also%20be%20a%20risk%20to%20people.%20Since%201997%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20has%20recommended%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20the%20agents%20of%20all%20known%20prion%20diseases%20from%20entering%20the%20human%20food%20chain%2C''%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fprions%2Fcwd%2Findex.html%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22URL%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fprions%2Fcwd%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECDC%20website%20reads%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%C2%A0Zombie%20Deer%20Disease%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Zombie%20Deer%20Disease'%20also%20known%20as%20Chronic%20wasting%20disease%20(CWD)%2C%20is%20a%20contagious%20and%20fatal%20illness%20that%20affects%20cervids%2C%20a%20group%20of%20animals%20that%20includes%20deer%2C%20elk%2C%20caribou%2C%20reindeer%2C%20and%20moose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20caused%20by%20a%20malformed%20protein%20(prion)%20which%20accumulates%20in%20the%20brain%20and%20other%20tissues%20causing%20physiological%20and%20behavioral%20changes%2C%20emaciation%2C%20and%20ultimately%20death.%C2%A0It%20is%20transmitted%20by%20direct%20animal-to-animal%20contact%20or%20indirectly%20through%20contact%20with%20infectious%20particles%20persisting%20in%20the%20environment%20such%20as%20feces%2C%20soil%2C%20or%20vegetation.%C2%A0Animals%20can%20also%20become%20infected%20if%20their%20feed%20or%20pasture%20is%20contaminated%20with%20the%20prions%20carrying%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20it%20may%20take%20over%20a%20year%20for%20symptoms%20in%20the%20deer%20to%20develop.%20It%20usually%20starts%20with%20the%20deer%20drastically%20losing%20weight%2C%20stumbling%20around%2C%20and%20losing%20all%20energy.%C2%A0At%20present%2C%20CWD%20does%20not%20have%20any%20cure%20or%20vaccine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703612820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Fp8dh2u5_spotted-deer-generic-pixabay_625x300_04_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fzombie-deer-disease-could-spread-to-humans-scientists-warn-as-cases-surge-in-us-4747606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Experts%20have%20labeled%20the%20disease%20as%20a%20''slow-moving%20disaster''%20and%20are%20strongly%20advising%20governments%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20likelihood%20of%20its%20transmission%20to%20humans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fzombie-deer-disease-could-spread-to-humans-scientists-warn-as-cases-surge-in-us-4747606%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fzombie-deer-disease-could-spread-to-humans-scientists-warn-as-cases-surge-in-us-4747606%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fzombie-deer-disease-could-spread-to-humans-scientists-warn-as-cases-surge-in-us-4747606%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Pens%20Scathing%20Obituary%20About%20%26quot%3BViolent%2C%20Hateful%20and%20Cruel%26quot%3B%20Mother%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20the%20United%20States%20wrote%20a%20scathing%20obituary%20about%20her%20%26quot%3Bviolent%2C%20hateful%2C%20and%20cruel%26quot%3B%20mother.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20obituary%20for%20Linda%20Lernal%20Harvey%20Cullum%20Smith%20Stull%2C%20which%20has%20been%20taken%20down%2C%20was%20written%20by%20her%2054-year-old%20daughter%20Gayle%20Harvey%20Heckman.%20In%20the%20obituary%2C%20Ms%20Gayle%20accused%20her%20mother%20of%20a%20series%20of%20abuses%20and%20wrongdoings.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20mother%2C%20Lernal%20was%20violent%2C%20hateful%2C%20and%20cruel.%20She%20physically%2C%20mentally%2C%20emotionally%2C%20verbally%2C%20and%20financially%20abused%20Gayle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20obituary%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLernal%20accused%20Gayle%20of%20'trying%20to%20steal%20her%20husband'%20and%20proceeded%20to%20beat%20her%20senselessly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20obituary%20continued.%20%26quot%3BGayle%20and%20her%20family%20forgive%20Lernal%20and%20hope%20that%20she%20has%20found%20peace.%20They%20also%20hope%20to%20find%20peace%20within%20themselves.%20Lernal%20will%20not%20be%20missed%20by%20Gayle%20or%20her%20family.%20They%20all%20understand%20the%20world%20is%20a%20much%20better%20place%20without%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0the%20piece%20concluded%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fdaughter-mother-obituary-abusive-b2469107.html%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20obituary%20was%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThree%20Rivers%20News%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethree%20days%20after%20Ms%20Lernal's%20death%20on%20December%2012.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20the%20paper%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20obituary%20was%20significantly%20shortened%20due%20to%20it%20just%20being%20a%20spiteful%20hate%20piece%20against%20a%20beloved%20member%20of%20our%20community%26quot%3B.%20The%20publication%20also%20revealed%20that%20Ms%20Gayle%20is%20Ms%20Lernal's%20first%20child.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gayle%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20explained%20why%20she%20wrote%20the%20obituary.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F12%2F22%2Fnews%2Fmichigan-woman-attacks-dead-mom-in-vicious-obituary%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0the%2054-year-old%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20honestly%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20write%20it%20for%20myself%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20clear%20my%20name.%20For%2024%20years%20and%20before%20that%2C%20my%20mother%20has%20had%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20reason%20as%20to%20why%20her%20daughter%20isn't%20in%20her%20life%20that%20doesn't%20make%20her%20look%20like%20a%20monster.%20...%20I%20had%20to%20reclaim%20my%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgo-back-to-pakistan-couple-tells-indian-origin-man-after-taking-over-his-us-home-4745963%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGo%20Back%20To%20Pakistan%26quot%3B%3A%20Couple%20Tells%20Indian-Origin%20Man%20After%20Taking%20Over%20His%20US%20Home%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gayle%20also%20stated%20that%20she%20wasn't%20trying%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bhateful%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20wrote%20the%20obituary%20but%20was%20expressing%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bangry%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20understand%20if%20we%20don't%20talk%20about%20this%2C%20how%20are%20we%20supposed%20to...%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20trauma%2C%20especially%20generational%20trauma%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMike%20Wilcox%2C%20publisher%20of%20%3Cem%3EWilcox%20Newspapers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20the%20obit%20ran%20in%20the%20print%20edition%20of%20Three%20Rivers%20on%20December%2015.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20submitted%20through%20our%20website%2C%20and%20was%20publishe