2Fstrong%3E%20Writing%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20that%20her%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20and%20her%20Arjuna%20Award%20no%20longer%20mean%20anything%20to%20her%2C%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20said%20she%20wishes%20to%20return%20the%20medals%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20woman%20wants%20to%20live%20with%20dignity.%20That%20is%20why%2C%20Mr%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20I%20wish%20to%20return%20my%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20and%20Arjuna%20Award%20to%20you%20%E2%80%93%20so%20that%20these%20prizes%20do%20not%20burden%20us%20on%20our%20path%20to%20living%20with%20dignity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Phogat%20wrote%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20and%20fellow%20wrestlers%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20were%20among%20the%20main%20faces%20of%20the%20protests%20earlier%20this%20year%20against%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20at%20least%20seven%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20quit%20wrestling%20and%20Punia%20gave%20away%20his%20Padma%20Shri%20medal%20last%20week%20after%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20a%20man%20backed%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20won%20elections%20to%20the%20WFI%20on%20Thursday%20(December%2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Phogat%20referred%20to%20Malik%20and%20Punia%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20and%20said%20she%20now%20felt%20revulsed%20by%20her%20own%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20year%202016%2C%20when%20%5BMalik%5D%20won%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20and%20the%20government%20made%20her%20the%20brand%20ambassador%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ebeti%20bachao%2C%20beti%20padhao%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%5Bcampaign%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20decision%20had%20sparked%20celebration%20among%20woman%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20%5BMalik%5D%20has%20had%20to%20quit%20wrestling%2C%20I%20am%20constantly%20reminded%20of%20the%20year%202016.%20Are%20we%20women%20athletes%20only%20fit%20to%20be%20published%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20advertisements%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20the%20lives%20of%20women%20athletes%20differed%20from%20how%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20posters%20depicted%20them%20to%20be%2C%20Phogat%20asked%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20out%20just%20five%20minutes%20of%20%5Bhis%5D%20life%E2%80%9D%20to%20listen%20to%20statements%20made%20in%20the%20media%20by%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20exploiter%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20Brij%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20likened%20women%20wrestlers%20to%20%E2%80%98Manthra%E2%80%99%20%5Ba%20deceitful%20character%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%2C%20has%20openly%20confessed%20on%20TV%20to%20making%20women%20wrestlers%20uncomfortable%20and%20has%20never%20given%20up%20an%20opportunity%20to%20humiliate%20women%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20more%20serious%20is%20how%20many%20women%20wrestlers%20he%20has%20forced%20out.%20This%20is%20very%20appalling%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%2C%20adding%20to%20say%20that%20wrestlers%20were%20hailed%20for%20winning%20medals%20but%20called%20traitors%20to%20the%20nation%20for%20raising%20their%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMr%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20ask%20you%2C%20are%20we%20traitors%3F%E2%80%9D%20Phogat%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20while%20she%20did%20not%20know%20what%20condition%20Punia%20was%20in%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20part%20with%20his%20Padma%20Shri%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20fourth-highest%20civilian%20award%20%E2%80%93%20she%20now%20felt%20disgusted%20by%20her%20own%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20now%20like%20to%20be%20rid%20of%20the%20image%20of%20Vinesh%20receiving%20her%20awards%2C%20as%20that%20was%20a%20dream%20while%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20us%20today%20is%20the%20reality.%20I%20was%20given%20the%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20and%20the%20Arjuna%20Award%2C%20which%20no%20longer%20mean%20anything%20in%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Phogat%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20published%20her%20letter%20in%20an%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20post%20on%20Tuesday%20(December%2026)%2C%20where%20she%20also%20thanked%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpowerful%E2%80%9D%20for%20bringing%20her%20to%20her%20current%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20public%20outrage%2C%20the%20sports%20ministry%20dissolved%20the%20new%20WFI%20under%20Sanjay%20Singh%20on%20Saturday%20(December%2024)%2C%20appearing%20to%20slam%20its%20lack%20of%20regard%20for%20norms%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20functions%20out%20of%20former%20officer%20bearers%20who%20are%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703608240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26214157%2FVinesh-Phogat.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvinesh-phogat-writes-to-pm-modi-returns-awards%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20her%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Phogat%20referred%20to%20Sakshi%20Malik's%20retirement%20from%20wrestling%20as%20well%20as%20Bajrang%20Punia's%20giving%20up%20his%20Padma%20Shri%2C%20and%20said%20she%20now%20felt%20revulsed%20by%20her%20own%20awards.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvinesh-phogat-writes-to-pm-modi-returns-awards%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Axis%20Bank%20files%20corporate%20insolvency%20plea%20against%20Zee%20Learn%20with%20NCLT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703608226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-04%2F27%2Ffull%2F1619523019-4025.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-st