20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%E2%81%A0The%20cut%20money%20collected%20from%20Bengal%20is%20used%20to%20buy%20palatial%20mansions%20in%20foreign%20countries%20but%20the%20same%20people%20roam%20around%20here%20in%20hawai%20chappal%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20rarely%20seen%20in%20anything%20except%20in%20her%20trademark%20white%20saree%20and%20rubber%20slippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah's%20visit%20comes%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20pinning%20its%20hopes%20on%20sweeping%20Bengal's%20parliamentary%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20a%20goal%20that%20stayed%20out%20of%20reach%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP's%20chief%20strategist%20predicted%20the%20party%20will%20win%20more%20than%2035%20of%20Bengal's%2040%20seats%20next%20year%20%E2%80%93%20up%20from%2018%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20party's%20IT%20cell%20will%20be%20pivotal%2C%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20because%20the%20regional%20media%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20carry%20the%20message%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20fearing%20Didi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%E2%81%A0If%20you%20all%20social%20media%20warriors%20decide%2C%20you%20can%20have%20more%20reach%20than%20any%20channel%20or%20newspaper%20and%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20you%20from%20making%20Modi-ji%20win.%20That%20is%20the%20reason%20you%20have%20the%20biggest%20responsibilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703604420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fhg06f8fs_amit-shah-pti_625x300_22_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdidis-mps-mimic-veep-share-password-amit-shah-in-meet-on-bengal-4746738%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20home%20minister%20and%20the%20BJP's%20chief%20strategist%20Amit%20Shah%20launched%20a%20no-holds%20barred%20attack%20on%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20today%2C%20accusing%20her%20MPs%20of%20gross%20misconduct%20and%20her%20government%20of%20keeping%20the%20state%20stagnant.%22%2C%22autho