w%20of%20majoritarian%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CPI(M)%20General%20Secretary%20Comrade%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20has%20received%20an%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20CPI(M)%20policy%20has%20been%20to%20respect%20religious%20beliefs%20and%20safeguarding%20the%20right%20of%20every%20individual%20to%20pursue%20their%20belief.%20It%20believes%20that%20religion%20is%20a%20personal%20choice%20not%20to%20be%20converted%20into%20an%20instrument%20for%20political%20gain.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20attending%20the%20ceremony%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CPI(M)%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20fundamental%20principle%20of%20governance%20in%20India%20as%20reiterated%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20that%20the%20State%20in%20India%2C%20under%20the%20constitution%20should%20have%20no%20religious%20affiliation.%20This%20is%20being%20violated%20by%20the%20ruling%20regime%20in%20the%20organisation%20of%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20trust%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fcpims-sitaram-yechury-turns-down-invitation-for-ram-temple-consecration-2823580%5C%22%3Eextended%20invitations%20to%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20party%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703593927000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F09141607%2F22.2.22-20.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcpim-turns-down-ram-temple-invite-says-religion-shouldnt-be-used-for-political-gain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20party%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20most%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20have%20converted%20a%20religious%20ceremony%20into%20a%20state%20sp