while%2C%20Dalit%20thinkers%20believe%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20is%20focusing%20more%20on%20Valmiki%20temples%20to%20engage%20the%20Dalit%20community%20with%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20grand%20ceremony%20and%20its%20Hindutva%20agenda.%20They%20think%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20attempting%20to%20woo%20the%20community%20by%20connecting%20them%20to%20these%20events%20to%20garner%20Dalit%20votes%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F690013%2Fwatch-ram-temple-india-democracy-pluralism-ram-guha-karan-thapar%2F%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20Tamasha%20Around%20Ram%20Temple%20Should%20Worry%20Indians%20Who%20Believe%20in%20Democracy%2C%20Pluralism%3A%20Ram%20Guha%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20there%20is%20a%20sizeable%20population%20of%20Dalits%2C%20nearly%2022%25%2C%20residing%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20that%20they%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20electoral%20politics%20of%20the%20state%20which%20sends%2080%20lawmakers%20to%20Loksabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20they%20are%20voters%20of%20the%20Mayawati-led%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20but%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20Dalits%2C%20especially%3Cem%3E%C2%A0non-Jatavs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20swayed%20into%20the%20saffron%20fold%20since%20the%20entry%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20into%20national%20politics.%20The%20BJP%20is%20looking%20to%20expand%20its%20outreach%20among%20other%20sections%20of%20Dalit%20society%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20that%20Yogi%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20focusing%20more%20on%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Valmiki%20temples%20to%20keep%20the%20caste%20group%20intact%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dalit%20thinker%20Ravikant%20Chandan.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20Valmiki%20community%20is%20already%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20fold%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20bring%20together%20other%20sections%20of%20the%20community%20under%20the%20pretence%20of%20%3Cem%3Eprana%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20at%20Lucknow%20University%2C%20Chandan%20also%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20perturbed%20about%20the%20Dalit%20votes%20as%20after%20the%20re-emergence%20of%20Ambedkarite%20movements%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Dalit%20youths%20are%20leaving%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20wants%20to%20engage%20Dalit%20youths%20in%20religious%20activities%20and%20suppress%20the%20question%20of%20their%20dignified%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20letter%20issued%20by%20the%20office%20of%20the%20chief%20secretary%2C%20these%20cultural%20events%20will%20start%20a%20week%20before%20the%20%3Cem%3Eprana%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Makar%20Sankranti.%20The%20government%20says%20the%20genesis%20behind%20organising%20these%20events%20based%20on%20the%20life%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Ram%20is%20to%20disseminate%20the%20idea%20of%20establishing%20the%20moral%2C%20social%2C%20and%20human%20values%20of%20Ram%20among%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%20which%20according%20to%20it%20are%20very%20relevant%20and%20important%20in%20the%20present%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-ayodhya-ram-temple-and-lk-advanis-sour-grapes-of-rath%5C%22%3EThe%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20LK%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20(Sour)%20Grapes%20of%20Rath%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%20also%20stated%20in%20his%20two-page%20letter%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20people%20have%20a%20very%20close%20attachment%20to%20this%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20birthplace.%20So%2C%20besides%20lamp%20lighting%20and%20donation%20of%20lamps%2C%20etc.%2C%20the%20district%20authorities%20should%20ensure%20continuous%20recitation%20of%20%3Cem%3ERam%20katha%2C%20Ramayana%2C%20Ramcharit%20Manas%2C%20Sunderkand%20%3C%2Fem%3Eetc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20IAS%20officer%20Vijay%20Shankar%20Pandey%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20current%20scenario%2C%20bureaucrats%20are%20ignoring%20the%20ethos%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20dancing%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20their%20political%20masters.%20It%20is%20well%20known%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20Movement%20was%20politically%20motivated%2C%20and%20it%20is%20crystal%20clear%20who%20is%20reaping%20the%20dividend.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandey%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992%20was%20an%20assault%20on%20our%20constitution.%20Nothing%20is%20objectionable%20in%20temple%20construction%20as%20it%20is%20allowed%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20of%20the%20country%20but%20the%20use%20of%20government%20machinery%20for%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20unjust%20and%20unfair%20practice%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20says%20an%20order%20was%20issued%20from%20power%20corridors%20of%20UP%20to%20ask%20the%20district%20authorities%20to%20organise%20a%20nine-day-long%20chain%20of%20events%3A%20a%20programme%20of%20s%3Cem%3Eankirtans%3C%2Fem%3E%20should%20be%20organised%20in%20the%20municipal%20bodies%20by%20including%20local%3Cem%3E%20bhajan-kirtan%3C%2Fem%3E%20groups%20and%20Ram%20temple%3Cem%3E%C2%A0rath%20and%20kalash%20yatras%3C%2Fem%3E%20should%20be%20organised%20in%20the%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20give%20priority%20to%20the%20artists%20and%3Cem%3E%20bhajan-kirtan%3C%2Fem%3E%20groups%20who%20are%20registered%20with%20the%20culture%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharat%20Pradhan%2C%20a%20senior%20political%20commentator%20who%20covered%20the%20Ayodhya%20movement%20extensively%20during%20the%20late%201980s%20and%20early%201990s%2C%20opined%20that%20the%20UP%20government%E2%80%99s%20circular%20is%20against%20the%20essence%20of%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1-300x205.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1-1024x699.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22819%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992.%20Photo%3A%20Sanjay%20Sharma%2FINDIAPIX%20NETWORK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20type%20of%20government%20involvement%20was%20never%20seen%20in%20the%20past%3B%20it%20is%20unprecedented%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pradhan.%20He%20sees%20this%20as%20a%20political%20game%20plan%20to%20transform%20secular%20India%20into%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20events%20successful%20at%20the%20district%2C%20tehsil%2C%20and%20block%20levels%2C%20district%20magistrates%20will%20seek%20assistance%20from%20Mahila%20Mangal%20Dal%2C%20Yuva%20Mangal%20Dal%2C%20and%20ASHA%20Bahus%20following%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20nod.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficers%20are%20also%20asked%20that%20after%20selecting%20the%20temples%2C%20their%20list%20and%20name%2C%20designation%2C%20address%2C%20mobile%20numbers%2C%20and%20name%20of%20the%20nodal%20officer%20should%20be%20uploaded%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fculturalevents.in%2Framotsav%5C%22%3Eculture%20department%E2%80%99s%20portal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20a%20part%20of%20their%20duty%20to%20provide%20the%20complete%20address%2C%20photo%2C%20GPS%20location%2C%20and%20contact%20number%20of%20the%20temple%20manager%20of%20the%20chosen%20temples%20in%20each%20district%20on%20the%20mentioned%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20of%20selecting%20temples%20for%20the%20event%20is%20assigned%20to%20local%20administrations%20and%20nominated%20nodal%20officers%20will%20monitor%20the%20events.%20The%20onus%20of%20publicity%20and%20propaganda%20for%20this%20mass%20event%20is%20on%20the%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%20Department%20and%20District%20Information%20Officers%20at%20the%20district%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20events%20will%20be%20organised%20only%20after%20obtaining%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20from%20the%20competent%20level.%20Directions%20were%20also%20issued%20for%20arrangements%20for%20cleanliness%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20security%2C%20carpet%20laying%2C%20sound%2C%20lighting%20(as%20per%20requirement)%2C%20refreshments%2C%20etc.%20at%20event%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Ahirwar%2C%20Assistant%20Director%20(General%2FPerforming%20Arts)%2C%20Directorate%20of%20Culture%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20nodal%20officer%20according%20to%20the%20chief%20secretary%E2%80%99s%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20Sheetal%20P.%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20undeclared%20or%20unofficial%20declaration%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20Such%20a%20decision%20will%20create%20a%20hostile%20situation%20for%20Muslims%2C%20although%20they%20are%20silent%20over%20this%20issue%20since%20they%20lost%20the%20legal%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703589620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fup-govt-asks-district-authorities-to-organise-ramayana-readings-