-india-13037610%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhundreds-of-indian-citizens-grounded-in-france-for-human-trafficking-investigation-land-in-india-13037610%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhundreds-of-indian-citizens-grounded-in-france-for-human-trafficking-investigation-land-in-india-13037610%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There%20Are%20Shades%20of%20the%20BCCI%20in%20the%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20Usman%20Khawaja%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26114543%2FUntitled-design-14-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20they%20know%20of%20cricket%20who%20only%20cricket%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20immortal%20sentence%20from%20C.L.R.%20James%20should%20be%20the%20guiding%20motto%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20farthest%20from%20their%20thoughts%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20latest%20sign%20is%20the%20case%20of%20Australian%20batter%20Usman%20Khawaja%20who%20was%20barred%20from%20wearing%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%20is%20a%20human%20right%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Call%20lives%20are%20equal%E2%80%9D%20on%20his%20shoes%20during%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Perth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThank%20you%20to%20all%20those%20who%20supported%20and%20gave%20me%20love%20this%20week.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20unnoticed%20%F0%9F%92%95.%20Nothing%20worthwhile%20is%20easy.%20History%20shows%20we%20are%20doomed%20to%20repeat%20the%20mistakes%20of%20our%20past.%20But%20together%20we%20can%20fight%20for%20a%20better%20future.%20%F0%9F%99%8F%F0%9F%8F%BE%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Ffreedomisahumanright%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23freedomisahumanright%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Falllivesareequal%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23alllivesareequal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHAhbebDbCT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHAhbebDbCT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Usman%20Khawaja%20(%40Uz_Khawaja)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUz_Khawaja%2Fstatus%2F1736680713657999851%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20had%20also%20copped%20a%20reprimand%20for%20having%20sported%20a%20black%20armband%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20Test%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20at%20Perth%20Stadium%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20ICC%20has%20gone%20further%20and%20rejected%20his%20application%20to%20spread%20his%20message%20of%20peace%20by%20sporting%20a%20dove%20with%20an%20olive%20branch%20on%20his%20shoe%20during%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20Article%20One%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%20that%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20human%20beings%20are%20born%20free%20and%20equal%20in%20dignity%20and%20rights.%20They%20are%20endowed%20with%20reason%20and%20conscience%20and%20should%20act%20towards%20one%20another%20in%20a%20spirit%20of%20brotherhood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhawaja%2C%20who%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20his%20beliefs%2C%20has%20the%20support%20of%20his%20cricket%20board%2C%20his%20captain%20Pat%20Cummins%20and%20teammates.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20really%20support%20Uzzy%20(Khawaja).%20I%20think%20he%E2%80%99s%20standing%20up%20for%20what%20he%20believes%2C%20and%20I%20think%20he%E2%80%99s%20doing%20it%20really%20respectfully%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20at%20a%20presser%2C%20Cummins%20argued%20that%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20Usman%20Khawaja%20displaying%20a%20dove%20logo%20on%20his%20shoe%20and%20bat%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20humanitarian%20issues%20and%20teammate%20Marnus%20Labuschagne%20displaying%20an%20eagle%20on%20his%20bat%20which%20signifies%20a%20personal%20religious%20message.%20Labuschagne%20displays%20the%20symbol%20of%20an%20eagle%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20bats%20which%20represents%20a%20verse%20from%20the%20bible%20and%20has%20long%20been%20allowed%20to%20have%20the%20sticker%20on%20his%20bat%20in%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20player%20in%20the%20Australian%20team%2C%20including%20Khawaja%2C%20also%20have%20multiple%20advertising%20stickers%20on%20their%20bats%20that%20represent%20different%20companies%20including%20their%20bat%2Fequipment%20sponsor%20and%20a%20secondary%20personal%20sponsor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20religious%20cause%20is%20acceptable%2C%20commercial%20gain%20is%20welcomed%20but%20a%20message%20for%20peace%20and%20humanity%20is%20not.%20The%20message%20is%20about%20Gaza%20where%20Israeli%20military%20action%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20including%208%2C000%20children.%20Khwaja%20is%20not%20wearing%20a%20Palestinian%20symbol%20or%20an%20Islamic%20motif.%20He%20is%20reminding%20the%20world%20of%20what%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%2C%20adopted%20after%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hypocrisy%20of%20those%20who%20constantly%20shouted%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20again%E2%80%9D%20and%20pledged%20to%20uphold%20the%20%E2%80%9Crules-based%20global%20order%E2%80%9D%20is%20laid%20bare%20by%20this%20simple%20gesture%20by%20Khwaja.%20It%20is%20way%20short%20of%20what%20was%20done%20to%20Russian%20athletes%20after%20Putin%20invaded%20Ukraine%3B%20or%20when%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20wore%20camouflage%20pattern%20caps%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20ICC%20should%20feel%20uncomfortable%20with%20Khwaja%E2%80%99s%20request%20is%20hard%20to%20comprehend.%20Cricket%20is%20a%20game%20mainly%20played%20by%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20barring%20England%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20where%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20has%20overwhelming%20support.%20South%20Africa%20and%20Ireland%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20those%20speaking%20against%20the%20horrors%20being%20inflicted%20upon%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%20India%20is%20the%20outlier%20here%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%20has%20embraced%20the%20US%20position%20rather%20closely%20and%20supported%20his%20friend%20Bibi%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20is%20sending%20Indian%20workers%20to%20replace%20the%20Palestinian%20labour%20working%20in%20the%20construction%20sector%20in%20Israel.%20His%20supporters%20remain%20in%20thrall%20of%20an%20Islamophobic%20narrative%2C%20which%20is%20reinforced%20by%20the%20Israeli%20state%20narrative%20about%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20party%20is%20a%20staunch%20supporter%20of%20Israel%20and%20avoids%20asking%20for%20peace%20and%20justice%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20occupied%20areas.%20It%20controls%20the%20BCCI%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20spiritual%20and%20material%20boss%20of%20the%20ICC.%20Is%20that%20the%20reason%20Khawaja%E2%80%99s%20request%20has%20been%20denied%20by%20the%20ICC%3F%20What%20else%20could%20be%20the%20reason%3F%20Meanwhile%2C%20here%20in%20India%2C%20forget%20current%20or%20former%20cricketers%2C%20even%20sports%20journalists%20are%20unwilling%20to%20underline%20the%20Khawaja%20episode%20lest%20it%20forces%20people%20to%20wonder%20why%20Indian%20cricket%20superstars%20are%20such%20cowards%20%E2%80%93%20and%20are%20subjugated%20into%20submission%20by%20those%20who%20now%20have%20parasitic%20control%20over%20Indian%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20for%20the%20ICC%2C%20peace%20and%20brotherhood%20is%20too%20much%20to%20ask%20for.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20cricket.%20Neither%20is%20it%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESushant%20Singh%20is%20Senior%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703571621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26114543%2FUntitled-design-14-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-usman-khawaja-icc-bcci-order%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20for%20the%20ICC%2C%20peace%20and%20brotherhood%20is%20too%20much%20to%20ask%20for.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20cricket.%20Neither%20is%20it%20humanity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A117%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-usman-khawaja-icc-bcci-order%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%3A%20Alexei%20Navalny%20Located%20in%20Siberia%20Prison%2C%20Allies%20Say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26105251%2Fimage-1-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAlexei%20Navalny%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdoing%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20spokeswoman%20Kira%20Yarmysh%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Russian%20opposition%20figure%20had%20been%20located%20in%20a%20penal%20colony%20in%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20far%20north%2C%20in%20the%20Yamalo-Nenets%20region%20of%20western%20Siberia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20critic%20has%20been%20missing%20for%20weeks%2C%20with%20many%20fearing%20for%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20found%20Alexey%20Navalny.%20He%20is%20now%20in%20IK-3%20settlement%20of%20Kharp%20in%20the%20Yamal-Nenets%20Autonomous%20District%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yarmysh%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%2C%20using%20alternative%20spellings%20for%20Navalny%20and%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20lawyer%20visited%20him%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts%20had%20been%20unknown%20since%20early%20December%2C%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20unable%20to%20reach%20him%2C%20and%20court%20appointments%20in%20the%20various%20cases%20against%20him%20had%20been%20delayed%20without%20authorities%20providing%20reasons%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20had%20prompted%20concern%20among%20his%20supporters%20and%20international%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConditions%20%E2%80%98brutal%E2%80%99%20in%20Polar%20Wolf%20camp%2C%20Navalny%20colleague%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20found%20Alexei!%E2%80%9D%20the%20manager%20of%20Navalny%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Corruption%20Foundation%20organisation%2C%20Ivan%20Zhdanov%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20IK-3%20facility%20was%20nicknamed%20the%20%E2%80%9CPolar%20Wolf%E2%80%9D%20prison%20camp%20and%20that%20it%20was%20among%20the%20most%20remote%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20conditions%20there%20are%20brutal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20According%20to%20Zhdanov%2C%20there%20is%20permafrost%20at%20the%20camp%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20to%20reach%20and%20no%20letters%20are%20delivered%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharp%20is%20a%20remote%20town%20of%20around%206%2C500%20people%2C%20according%20to%20a%202010%20census%2C%20in%20the%20Ural%20mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhdanov%20said%20the%20move%20should%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20He%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20Kremlin%20of%20trying%20to%20isolate%20Navalny%20ahead%20of%20the%20presidential%20election%20on%20March%2017%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fvladimir-putin%2Ft-17449200%5C%22%3EVladimir%20Putin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20win%20another%20term.%20This%20would%20be%20his%20fifth%20as%20president%20with%20a%20period%20as%20prime%20minister%20between%202008%20and%202012.%20Term%20limit%20rules%20have%20been%20abolished%20in%20Russia%20with%20relative%20ease%20since%20Putin%20first%20took%20power%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%20was%20previously%20being%20held%20in%20the%20IK-6%20prison%20facility%2C%20a%20comparatively%20short%20distance%20southeast%20of%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20%E2%80%98deeply%20concerned%E2%80%99%20over%20Navalny%E2%80%99s%20state%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20condemned%20Navalny%E2%80%99s%20detention%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunjust%E2%80%9D%20and%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20conditions%20in%20the%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20remain%20deeply%20concerned%20for%20Mr.%20Navalny%E2%80%99s%20wellbeing%20and%20the%20conditions%20of%20his%20unjust%20detention%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20while%20adding%20that%20the%20State%20Department%20welcomes%20reports%20that%20he%20had%20been%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmalicious%20targeting%E2%80%9D%20of%20Navalny%20and%20called%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20release%2C%20without%20conditions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20call%20on%20the%20Russian%20government%20to%20end%20its%20escalating%20repression%20of%20independent%20voices%20in%20Russia%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArrested%20in%202021%20after%20recovery%20from%202020%20poisoning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%2C%2047%2C%20made%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20by%20publicly%20calling%20out%20corruption%20at%20the%20Kremlin%2C%20and%20first%20made%20a%20run%20to%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmoscow%2Ft-19038132%5C%22%3EMoscow%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20mayor%20in%202013.%20He%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Anti-Corruption%20Foundation%2C%20known%20in%20Russia%20as%20the%20FBK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faced%20repeated%20arrests%2C%20physical%20attacks%2C%20and%20various%20investigations%20and%20criminal%20proceedings%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fnavalnys-latest-conviction-purely-political-allies-say%2Fa-66430050%5C%22%3Ehe%20described%20as%20politically%20motivated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20his%20earlier%20years%20of%20political%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%20he%20survived%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Frussia-alexei-navalnys-german-doctors-detail-poison-treatment%2Fa-56045644%5C%22%3EGerman%20doctors%20said%20was%20a%20case%20of%20attempted%20poisoning%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20Soviet-era%20nerve%20agent%2C%20Novichok.%20Comatose%2C%20he%20was%20flown%20to%20Germany%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Russian%20officials%20then%20warned%20that%20his%20convalescence%20in%20Germany%20violated%20the%20terms%20of%20his%20probation%20for%20a%20prior%20conviction.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Falexei-navalnys-detainment-is-utterly-incomprehensible-says-germanys-maas%2Fa-56257961%5C%22%3ENavalny%20was%20arrested%20on%20his%20return%20early%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20first%20charged%20for%20violating%20the%20terms%20of%20his%20parole%2C%20but%20this%20was%20soon%20followed%20by%20charges%20of%20embezzlement%20and%20contempt%20of%20court%2C%20with%20a%20nine-year%20prison%20sentence.%20In%20August%20he%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20a%20series%20of%20extremism-related%20charges%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fnavalny-russia-opposition-leader-gets-19-more-years-in-jail%2Fa-66437898%5C%22%3Eand%20had%20his%20sentence%20extended%20to%2019%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20verdict%20also%20came%20with%20a%20court%20recommendation%20to%20relocate%20him%20to%20a%20more%20secure%2C%20harsher%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Frussia-alexei-navalny-located-in-siberia-prison-allies-say%2Fa-67819985%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703570687000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26105251%2Fimage-1-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frussia-alexei-navalny-located-in-siberia-prison-allies-say%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Russian%20opposition%20leader's%20lawyer%20was%20granted%20access%20to%20the%20politician.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frussia-alexei-navalny-located-in-siberia-prison-allies-say%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plane%20Held%20in%20France%20Over%20'Trafficking'%20Suspicions%20Lands%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F13173410%2F2018-06-13T105751Z_1_LYNXMPEE5C0Q1_RTROPTP_4_INDIA-AIRLINES.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20charter%20flight%20with%20303%20passengers%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20Indians%2C%20which%20was%20grounded%20for%20over%20four%20days%20in%20France%20over%20suspicions%20that%20the%20passengers%20were%20being%20trafficked%20has%20returned%20to%20India%20and%20landed%20in%20Mumbai%20at%204%20am%20today%2C%20December%2026%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20reported%20that%20276%20of%20the%20passengers%20have%20returned%20in%20the%20plane%20and%20that%2025%20have%20remained%20in%20France%2C%20seeking%20asylum%20status%20there.%20Two%20more%20have%20been%20held%2C%20%E2%80%9Cproduced%20before%20a%20judge%20and%20placed%20on%20assisted%20witness%20status%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20has%20noted%