llings%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20death%20toll%20of%20more%20than%202%2C000%20Balochs.%20According%20to%20activists%2C%20since%202021%2C%20over%20200%20Balochs%20have%20been%20murdered%20in%20fake%20encounters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-baloch-women-protest-extrajudicial-killings-forced-disappearances%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20Files%20Case%20Against%20ED%20for%20Preventing%20Anti-Corruption%20Officers%20From%20Doing%20Their%20Duty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29180215%2FThe-Wire-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20have%20reportedly%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20others%20for%20allegedly%20preventing%20investigators%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption%20(DVAC)%20from%20discharging%20their%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20summoned%20Brijesh%20Beniwal%2C%20Assistant%20Director%2C%20ED%2C%20Madurai%20sub-zonal%20office%2C%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Tallakulam%20police%20station%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fbribery-case-tn-cops-ask-ed-officer-to-appear-at-police-station-on-dec-26-2824801%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tensions%20between%20the%20ED%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20escalated%20after%20the%20police%20had%20arrested%20an%20ED%20official%20in%20the%20state.%20On%20December%201%2C%20the%20state%20police%20arrested%20ED%20official%20Ankit%20Tiwari%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20been%20caught%20%E2%80%9Cred-handed%E2%80%9D%20while%20accepting%20a%20bribe%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20from%20a%20doctor%20in%20the%20Dindigul%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20along%20with%20his%20team%20of%20ED%20officers%20had%20allegedly%20been%20threatening%20several%20people%20and%20receiving%20bribes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20closing%20their%20case%20at%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20police%20stated.%20DVAC%20officials%20caught%20him%20with%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20cash%20in%20Dindigul.%20DVAC%20also%20searched%20the%20ED%20Office%20in%20Madurai.%20Tiwari%20is%20still%20in%20jail%2C%20having%20been%20denied%20bail%20by%20both%20the%20trial%20court%20and%20the%20Madras%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Ftamil-nadu-police-register-case-against-ed-officials-for-preventing-dvac-investigators-from-discharging-their-duties%2Farticle67671891.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20fresh%20case%20filed%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20against%20in%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20police%20claim%20that%20the%20ED%20refused%20to%20allow%20DVAC%20officials%20to%20search%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20offices%20after%20his%20arrest%20on%20December%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Madurai%20city%20police%20that%20the%20DVAC%20search%20team%20was%20prevented%20from%20entering%20the%20chamber%20of%20accused%20officer%20Ankit%20Tiwari%20for%20more%20than%20three%20hours.%20The%20Assistant%20Director%20informed%20that%20the%20Deputy%20Director%20was%20in%20Chennai%20and%20was%20air%20dashing%20to%20Madurai%20to%20approve%20the%20search.%20But%20he%20did%20not%20come%E2%80%A6%20we%20had%20to%20seek%20the%20assistance%20of%20the%20local%20police%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20search%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20DVAC%20official%20told%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20too%20claims%20to%20be%20probing%20both%20Tiwari%20as%20well%20as%20officers%20of%20the%20DVAC.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fed-vs-tn-cops-agency-shifts-case-to-delhi-hq%2Farticleshow%2F106276481.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20moved%20this%20probe%20out%20of%20the%20state%20to%20its%20New%20Delhi%20headquarters.%20ED%20sources%20reportedly%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20this%20was%20because%20of%20fears%20of%20meddling%20from%20the%20local%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20claims%20had%20previously%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20DVAC%20officers%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%2C%20which%20did%20not%20register%20an%20FIR.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fbribery-case-tn-cops-ask-ed-officer-to-appear-at-police-station-on-dec-26-2824801%5C%22%3Emedia%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Beniwal%E2%80%99s%20complaints%20from%20December%202%20had%20accused%20the%20DVAC%20team%20of%20accessing%20sensitive%20case%20records%2C%20information%20and%20internal%20documents%20of%20the%20ED%20related%20to%20other%20cases%20which%20have%20no%20link%20with%20the%20alleged%20search%20case%2C%20and%20ransacking%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20entire%20office%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20officers%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20received%20no%20such%20complaint%20from%20the%20ED%20on%20that%20date.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20states%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20December%2016%2C%202023%2C%20a%20reminder%20letter%20requesting%20action%20was%20received%20by%20the%20DGP%E2%80%99s%20office%20wherein%20the%20original%20complaint%20was%20enclosed.%20The%20DGP%20forwarded%20the%20reminder%20enclosed%20with%20the%20original%20complaint%20to%20the%20Madurai%20Police%20Commissioner%20to%20conduct%20a%20detailed%20inquiry%20and%20send%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20the%20inquiry%2C%20the%20Madurai%20Police%20Commissioner%20sent%20a%20letter%20calling%20the%20ED%20officials%20to%20give%20evidence%20to%20substantiate%20their%20allegations.%20But%20they%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20letter%20and%20insisted%20that%20the%20same%20be%20sent%20by%20post.%20We%20then%20sent%20the%20letter%20by%20registered%20post%E2%80%A6%20there%20is%20no%20response%20yet.%20They%20have%20not%20turned%20up%20for%20the%20inquiry%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20not%20correct%20to%20say%20that%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20on%20ED%E2%80%99s%20complaint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703568494000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29180215%2FThe-Wire-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftamil-nadu-police-files-case-against-ed-for-preventing-anti-corruption-officers-from-doing-their-duty%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20have%20also%20summoned%20Brijesh%20Beniwal%2C%20Assistant%20Director%2C%20ED%2C%20Madurai%20sub-zonal%20office%2C%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Tallakulam%20police%20station.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftamil-nadu-police-files-case-against-ed-for-preventing-anti-corruption-officers-from-doing-their-duty%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Afghan%20couples%20marry%20in%20mass%20ceremony%20in%20bid%20to%20cut%20costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703568493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F220A%2Fproduction%2F_132141780_gettyimages-1874642533.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67821162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Such%20wedding%20ceremonies%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%20as%20couples%20seek%20to%20save%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A120%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67821162%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67821162.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67821162.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Mood%20For%20Murder%20%7C%20Episode%202%3A%20Roti%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24075850%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-23-at-12.13.33-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20series%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-1-tea%5C%22%3EEpisode%201%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs.%20Pushpa%20Kumari%20was%20a%20proud%20member%20of%20the%20Janawadi%20Mahila%20Sangathan%20and%20expected%20her%20husband%2C%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%20though%20he%20was%2C%20to%20help%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20He%20was%20laying%20the%20table%20and%20flipping%20TV%20channels%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20He%20settled%20on%20a%20loud%20and%20shrieking%20report%20about%20Muslims%20unfairly%20taking%20a%20disproportionate%20number%20of%20jobs%20in%20the%20Indian%20bureaucracy%20and%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUff%2C%20you%20have%20put%20on%20this%20idiotic%20channel%20again%3F%20This%20man%20just%20makes%20things%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20Jamal%20while%20I%20was%20on%20duty%20at%20a%20protest%20today.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20him%20%E2%80%93%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20such%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebadtameez%3C%2Fem%3E%20earlier.%20Spends%20his%20entire%20day%20going%20from%20one%20useless%20meeting%20to%20another.%20I%20told%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20career%2C%20and%20he%20started%20shouting%20at%20me%20in%20front%20of%20my%20juniors.%20Muslim%20boys%20are%20reacting%20badly%20to%20any%20mention%20of%20their%20careers%20and%20this%20channel%20is%20telling%20us%20that%20they%20are%20capturing%20the%20civil%20services!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20who%20has%20any%20career%20these%20days%2C%20except%20the%20rich!%20Our%20boys%20are%20going%20around%20doing%20%3Cem%3Edeshbhakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20streets.%20Their%20boys%20are%20protesting.%20Achcha%2C%20first%20you%20change%20the%20channel.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20see%20this%20stupid%20man%20while%20I%20am%20eating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20brought%20out%20the%20rotis%20from%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20Aamna%20is%20worried%20about%20Jamal.%20Their%20only%20son!%20He%20could%20easily%20have%20gone%20abroad.%20Aamna%20was%20talking%20about%20him%20at%20the%20party%20office%20yesterday%2C%20and%20didi%20said%20to%20us%20that%20our%20children%20are%20too%20sensitive%20for%20the%20present%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20children%20are%20sensible%20also%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20sensitive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20was%20coughing%20fitfully%20when%20Amma%20flung%20open%20the%20door%20to%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHide%20in%20your%20room%20and%20have%20more%20cigarettes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20air.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmma%20rolled%20her%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20that%20Achche%20bhai%20is%20like%20a%20brother%20to%20me.%20Pushpa%20and%20I%20are%20like%20sisters.%20You%20insulted%20him%20in%20public%3F%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20hear%20any%20excuses.%20Get%20up%20right%20now%2C%20go%20and%20bring%20rotis%20from%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20shop.%20Achche%20bhai%20will%20come%20for%20lunch%20and%20you%20will%20apologise%20to%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%20swatted%20at%20a%20single%20fly%20and%20managed%20to%20kill%20two.%20He%20was%20really%20quite%20large%2C%20but%20always%20underestimated%20his%20own%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20%3Cem%3Enehari%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%2C%20along%20the%20open%20gutter%2C%20two%20mangy%20dogs%20fought%20over%20some%20bones%20and%20gristle%2C%20while%20the%20onion%20skin%20and%20rotting%20lemon%20peels%20lay%20unheeded.%20Laadley%20Khan%2C%20the%20proprietor%20of%20that%20shop%2C%20sat%20cross-legged%20on%20a%20large%20Neelkamal%20plastic%20chair%2C%20behind%20a%20small%20aluminium%20counter%2C%20and%20stared%20at%20this%20scene.%20Suddenly%2C%20he%20made%20the%20connection%3A%20%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20thrown%20the%20muck%20just%20outside%20my%20door.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20place%20is%20infested%20with%20flies.%E2%80%9D%20He%20glared%20at%20his%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20establishment%20was%20situated%20in%20a%20narrow%2C%20winding%20alley%20in%20the%20old%20city.%20Ancient%20havelis%2C%20now%20partitioned%20and%20for%20the%20most%20part%20decrepit%2C%20blocked%20the%20sun%20and%20sky.%20It%20was%20often%20said%20that%20their%20old%20inhabitants%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20had%20had%20to%20leave%20them%20for%20Lahore%2C%20pined%20for%20them.%20Laadley%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20never%20gone%20anywhere.%20From%20his%20position%20of%20vantage%2C%20the%20chair%20upon%20which%20he%20remained%20perched%2C%20he%20keenly%20guarded%20the%20alley.%20He%20now%20saw%20a%20thickset%20man%20emerge%20from%20the%20grey%20smog%20and%20walk%20up%20quickly%2C%20purposefully.%20Laadley%20peered%20suspiciously%20at%20the%20figure%20until%20he%20recognised%20him%3A%20%E2%80%9COh%2C%20Jamal%20bhai!%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20himself.%20Jamal%20dodged%20the%20garbage%20and%20the%20scavengers%20and%20called%20out%20as%20he%20entered%20the%20shop%2C%20%E2%80%9CAre%20my%20rotis%20ready%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%20had%20always%20been%20burly%2C%20but%20had%20only%20recently%20become%20bearded.%20Patting%20his%20beard%2C%20he%20smiled%20at%20Jamal%20and%2C%20turning%20towards%20the%20tandoor%20to%20his%20right%2C%20barked%2C%20%E2%80%9CBring%20Jamal%20bhai%E2%80%99s%20packets!%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20observed%20him%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20and%20enquired%20casually%3A%20%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20hennaed%20your%20beard%2C%20Laadley%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20Khan%20blushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slightly%20built%20man%2C%20wearing%20a%20checked%20lungi%20and%20a%20sleeveless%20brown%20sweater%2C%20was%20hunched%20over%20the%20clay%20oven.%20He%20got%20up%20silently%20and%20handed%20Jamal%20a%20stack%20of%20greasy%20brown%20paper%20packets%20that%20smelled%20of%20tandoori%20roti%20and%20kabab.%20Jamal%20leaned%20back%20as%20he%20adjusted%20them%20against%20his%20chest.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20love%20of%20Allah%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20have%20the%20place%20swept%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99d%20very%20much%20like%20to%20have%20the%20place%20swept%2C%20Jamal%20bhai%2C%20but%20what%20will%20I%20do%20with%20the%20trash%3F%20The%20municipal%20cart%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20all%20the%20way%20here%2C%20does%20it%3F%20Every%20bastard%20is%20turning%20vegetarian%20suddenly.%20Nobody%20wants%20to%20touch%20animal%20filth%2C%20it%20seems.%20Not%20even%20the%20thieving%20%3Cem%3Emehtars%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%E2%80%99d%20have%20the%20waste%20thrown%20into%20the%20municipal%20dump%20on%20the%20main%20road%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99d%20just%20lie%20there%20also%2C%20and%20then%20everyone%20will%20get%20upset%20with%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20say%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20my%20garbage%2C%20let%20it%20just%20stay%20here.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchcha%3F%20And%20what%20will%20people%20think%20when%20they%20come%20to%20eat%20your%20nehari%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20comes%20to%20eat%20my%20nehari%3F%20Everyone%20buys%20rotis%20from%20me%20and%20then%20goes%20to%20Rahman%20Miyan%E2%80%99s%20fancy%20restaurant%20to%20eat%20his%20famous%20paya.%20All%20the%20big%20people%20go%20there%2C%20and%20the%20foreigners%20too.%20Only%20some%20local%20friends%20like%20you%20and%20Habib%20bhai%20come%20here%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20there%20is%20no%20obligation%20on%20you%20to%20keep%20your%20shop%20clean%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COho%20Jamal%20bhai.%20Locals%20are%20more%20troublesome%2C%20I%20must%20say.%20Arrey%2C%20the%20Angrez%20are%20simple%20people.%20They%20come%20here%20to%20see%20the%20old%20city%2C%20eat%20nehari%2C%20not%20to%20complain%20about%20the%20garbage.%20Do%20you%20know%2C%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20a%20%3Cem%3Efirangi%3C%2Fem%3E%20came%20to%20my%20shop%3F%20He%20had%20been%20walking%20around%20the%20old%20city%20and%20he%20came%20here%20for%20lunch%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20a%20word%20about%20the%20rubbish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20minions%20nodded%20in%20agreement%3A%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20the%20firangi%20was%20very%20cultured.%20He%20folded%20his%20hands%20and%20said%20%3Cem%3Enamaste%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3B%20everyone%20cackled%20at%20the%20firangi%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20faux%20pas%20and%20Jamal%20grinned%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20our%20Mullah%20ji%2C%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20even%20tried%20to%20correct%20him.%20He%20said%20sternly%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EWe%3C%2Fem%3E%20say%20salaam%20aleikum%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20poor%20man%20got%20very%20confused.%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20clapped%20his%20thighs%20in%20mirth%20and%20the%20assistants%20continued%20to%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Jamal%20had%20left%20the%20shop%20with%20his%20packets%2C%20Laadley%20Khan%20turned%20towards%20the%20tandoor%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CListen%2C%20swine%2C%20collect%20this%20rubbish%20now%20and%20throw%20it%20into%20the%20dump.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20see%20this%20mess%20in%20front%20of%20my%20shop.%E2%80%9D%20The%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%20appeared%20largely%20unaffected%2C%20so%20Laadley%20Khan%20continued%20to%20glower%20at%20him%2C%20his%20mouth%20slightly%20open%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20right%3F%20You%20heard%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20I%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Achche%20Lal.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20front%20of%20my%20juniors%2C%20he%20said%20that%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20I%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20being%20a%20wastrel.%20That%20I%20was%20a%20jihadi%2C%20and%20a%20bad%20son.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsghar%20and%20Aamna%20sat%20next%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20divan%2C%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20not%20laugh..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20said%20you%20are%20a%20Jihadi.%20I%20did%20say%20you%20are%20wasting%20your%20time.%20Your%20father%20retired%20from%20the%20examination%20section%20at%20Jamia.%20He%20has%20helped%20so%20many%20people%20from%20your%20community%20in%20getting%20pass%20marks.%20But%20his%20own%20son%20is%20now%20failing%20his%20exams.%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20stopped%20for%20a%20quick%20breadth%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20you%20just%20look%20at%20your%20health!%20Who%20gets%20sugar%20at%20your%20age%3F%20And%20even%20then%20you%20are%20not%20being%20careful.%20His%20friend%20was%20saying%20that%20because%20of%20his%20sugar%20he%20suddenly%20gets%20angry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsghar%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20to%20intervene.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20apologise%20to%20your%20chacha.%20Achche%20has%20carried%20you%20on%20his%20shoulders%20at%20so%20many%20of%20our%20rallies.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20dare%20presume%20to%20teach%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPushpa%20carried%20him.%20I%20was%20usually%20on%20duty%20by%20the%20time%20he%20was%20born.%20Of%20course%20in%20our%20student%20days%20we%20went%2C%20but%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20born%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20%3Cem%3Ehe%3C%2Fem%3E%20went%20to%20rallies%20as%20a%20student%2C%20then%20it%20was%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20grumbled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20times%20are%20different%20now.%20When%20we%20held%20rallies%2C%20it%20was%20for%20nation%20building%2C%20not%20for%20anti-national%20things.%20There%20were%20no%20hidden%20agendas%2C%20no%20international%20funding%20and%20toolkits%20to%20brainwash%20people%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20get%20arrested%20and%20then%20my%20parents%20would%20go%20crying%20to%20him%20for%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20we%20would%20go%20to%20him%20for%20help.%20One%20asks%20ones%20closest%20family%20only%20for%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Aamna.%20%E2%80%9CStop%20arguing%20with%20your%20chacha.%20Go%20put%20the%20rotis%20out.%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20unfolded%20his%20legs%20and%20reluctantly%20rose%20from%20his%20seat.%20She%20waited%20for%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20room%20and%20then%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CAchche%20bhai%2C%20you%20also%20start%20arguing%20as%20if%20you%20were%20the%20same%20age%20as%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20at%20all%20acting%20his%20age.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20tell%20him%20to%20get%20into%20some%20government%20department%2C%20preferably%20the%20police%20force.%20He%20would%20be%20able%20to%20help%20himself%20and%20his%20community%20much%20better%20that%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20your%20right%20and%20your%20duty%20to%20point%20him%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20Achche.%20But%20tell%20me%20frankly%2C%20how%20many%20Muslims%20are%20there%20in%20your%20own%20thana%3F%20How%20many%20SHOs%20are%20Muslim%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Asghar%20quietly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20you%20have%20to%20at%20least%20try%20to%20get%20into%20the%20system.%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20said%20irritably.%20He%20later%20told%20Pushpa%20that%20they%20are%20becoming%20too%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20becoming%20negative%3F%20Asghar%20bhai%2C%20or%20the%20entire%20Muslim%20community%3F%E2%80%9D%20Pushpa%20laughed.%20%E2%80%9CMore%20important%2C%20did%20you%20ask%20Jamal%20to%20come%20home%20on%20Diwali%3F%20He%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20him%20separately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20sat%20on%20a%20wooden%20bench%2C%20which%20was%20chained%20to%20the%20collapsible%20grill%20of%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar.%20The%20shop%20had%20sold%20crisp%20kachauris%20and%20jalebis%20and%20milky%20tea%20since%201949.%20The%20boys%20had%20been%20rocking%20the%20bench%20when%20Shambhu%2C%20the%20owner%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20came%20rushing%20out%20and%20yelled%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20do%20that!%20You%E2%80%99ll%20break%20the%20bench.%20Anyway%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20meant%20for%20patrons%2C%20not%20for%20freeloaders%20to%20lounge%20on.%E2%80%9D%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20in%20mild%20embarrassment%20and%20Kanwal%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20have%20some%20tea%2C%20in%20that%20case.%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20muttered%20something%20under%20his%20breath%20and%20went%20back%20into%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoss%2C%20it%20is%20not%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nirmal%20to%20Kanwal.%20%E2%80%9DWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20sit%20anywhere%20in%20peace.%20Constantly%20have%20to%20be%20buying%20something.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20westernisation%2C%20boss.%20Western%20consumerism%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kanwal%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20right.%20In%20the%20old%20days%20people%20could%20sit%20anywhere%3B%20they%20would%20be%20offered%20tea.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sense%20of%20%3Cem%3Eatithi%20devo%20bhava%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20no%20pride%20in%20our%20culture%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Nirmal%20stopped%20mid-sentence%2C%20and%20nudged%20Kanwal%3A%20%E2%80%9CBoss%2C%20see%20what%20he%20is%20doing!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slightly%20built%20man%20wearing%20a%20checked%20lungi%20and%20sleeveless%20sweater%20had%20emptied%20a%20bucket%20just%20outside%20the%20low%20boundary%20of%20the%20municipal%20dump.%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20could%20make%20out%20several%20bones%20and%20some%20gr