%2C%20forming%20a%20crowd%20behind%20him.%20Amongst%20them%20was%20Salman%2C%20the%20local%20delinquent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20going%20on%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20threw%20the%20waste%20into%20the%20dump%20just%20as%20you%20told%20me%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%20started%20chasing%20me%20and%20abusing%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20slightly%20built%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20go%20inside.%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20Khan%20said%20to%20him%2C%20and%20then%20turned%20towards%20Kanwal%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaan%20bhai%3F%20What%20is%20the%20problem%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20for%20encouragement%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20won%E2%80%99t%20allow%20desecration%20of%20our%20land%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20dump%20is%20your%20land%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20no%20animal%20slaughter%20in%20our%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%2C%20his%20feet%20wide%20apart%20and%20arms%20akimbo%2C%20frowned%20exaggeratedly%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20his%20audience%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20area%3F%C2%A0%20How%20is%20this%20your%20area%3F%20Your%20sister%20is%20married%20to%20Srivastava%20ji%E2%80%99s%20son.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20come%20from%20some%20village%20to%20live%20in%20your%20sister%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20study%2C%20and%20this%20has%20become%20%3Cem%3Eyour%3C%2Fem%3E%20area%3F%20My%20ancestors%20are%20buried%20here%20%E2%80%93%20permanently%20%E2%80%93%20not%20like%20you.%E2%80%9D%20The%20rearguard%20hooted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20regarded%20Laadley%20Khan%20with%20distaste.%20He%20wore%20a%20filthy%20shalwar-kameez%2C%20with%20the%20shalwar%20tied%20high%20and%20reaching%20his%20ankles.%20He%20also%20had%20a%20ridiculous%20henna-coloured%20beard%2C%20which%20provoked%20Kanwal%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20country%20is%20ours.%20You%20can%20go%20to%20Pakistan%20if%20you%20want!%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20and%20made%20as%20if%20to%20charge.%20Nirmal%20held%20him%20back%20and%20said%2C%20pacifyingly%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20our%20people%20win.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20then%20put%20them%20all%20in%20a%20municipal%20cart%2C%20with%20all%20the%20rubbish%2C%20and%20send%20them%20where%20they%20belong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%20looked%20gleeful%20as%20he%20readied%20himself%20for%20a%20fight.%20There%20were%20catcalls%20from%20his%20customers%20and%20his%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20drunk%20your%20mother%E2%80%99s%20milk%2C%20come%20here%20and%20fight!%E2%80%9D%20Salman%20pumped%20his%20chest%20and%20called%20out.%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%2C%20who%20were%20poised%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20alley%2C%20yelled%20back%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20come%20out%20some%20time%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20you%3F%20We%E2%80%99ll%20show%20you%20then.%20We%20remember%20all%20your%20faces%2C%20you%20bastards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAm%20I%20scared%20of%20you%2C%20you%20little%20twerp%3F%E2%80%99%20Laadley%20Khan%20roared%20as%20he%20started%20to%20walk%20towards%20them.%20At%20that%20fortuitous%20moment%2C%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20of%20Thana%20Sadar%20appeared%20at%20the%20junction%20of%20the%20road%20and%20alley%2C%20followed%20closely%20by%20Jamal%2C%20whose%20parents%20had%20insisted%20that%20he%20walk%20Achche%20chacha%20to%20the%20auto%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20happening%3F%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20asked%20sternly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20you%20only%20said%20to%20throw%20away%20the%20garbage.%20I%20told%20you%20the%20municipal%20cart%20never%20comes%20into%20our%20gali%2C%20and%20when%20we%20throw%20garbage%20on%20the%20main%20road%2C%20then%20these%20people%20throw%20tantrums.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20doing%20this%20to%20provoke%20us.%20He%20is%20showing%20us%20slaughtered%20animals!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kanwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20that%20offend%20you%20suddenly%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20turned%20to%20look%20at%20the%20heap%20that%20had%20been%20deposited.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20even%20inside%20the%20dump%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20emptied%20it%20on%20the%20street%2C%20literally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20inside%20only%2C%E2%80%9D%20whimpered%20the%20slightly%20built%20man%20from%20within%20the%20alley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20got%20a%20toehold%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWho%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20thrown%20all%20this%20outside%20the%20designated%20spot%3F%20Hup%2C%20come%20here!%E2%80%9D%20he%20barked%20at%20the%20slightly%20built%20man.%20The%20man%20retreated%20further%20into%20the%20dark%20recesses%20of%20the%20alley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20throws%20it%20there.%20If%20you%20throw%20it%20close%20enough%20to%20the%20dump%2C%20everyone%20understands%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20garbage.%20And%20anyway%2C%20why%20did%20they%20have%20to%20go%20prodding%20to%20look%20at%20what%20was%20there%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20Khan%20scowled%20back.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20say%20anything%20to%20those%20two%20troublemakers%2C%20Inspector%20saheb%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20I%20arrest%20you%20only%20Laadley%3F%20We%20have%20to%20first%20investigate%20whether%20there%20has%20been%20any%20illegal%20slaughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20snapped%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchche%20chacha%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20say%20such%20things.%20It%20is%20a%20sensitive%20matter.%20If%20you%20say%20it%20lightly%20even%2C%20people%20will%20believe%20it%20to%20be%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20whispered%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EChaliye%2C%20aap%20log%20bhi%20chaliye%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20pointed%20his%20chin%20at%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%20Then%20he%20gestured%20towards%20the%20alley%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20letting%20them%20be%20because%20of%20you%20Jamal%2C%20otherwise%20one%20or%20two%20deserve%20to%20be%20in%20jail.%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20glanced%20at%20Laadley%2C%20but%20let%20his%20eyes%20rest%20on%20Salman.%20He%20then%20took%20a%20few%20quick%20strides%20and%20left%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20began%20walking%20back%20towards%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar.%20Shambhu%20had%20come%20out%20of%20the%20shop%2C%20and%20was%20watching%20them%20with%20admiration.%20Halfway%2C%20they%20stopped%20again%2C%20turned%20around%20and%20yelled%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20get%20boys%20from%20the%20university%3B%20they%E2%80%99ll%20teach%20you%20to%20hurt%20peoples%E2%80%99%20sentiments%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20break%20all%20your%20bones%2C%20you%20scoundrel.%20They%20have%20been%20sent%20here%20to%20study%2C%20but%20all%20they%20do%20is%20create%20trouble%20and%20waste%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20yelled%20Laadley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20say%2C%20Laadley%20bhai%2C%20they%20are%20just%20frustrated%20because%20they%20are%20single.%20All%20the%20frustration%20is%20coming%20out%20like%20this.%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20have%20them%20blessed%20at%20the%20dargah%2C%20they%20might%20find%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%20Salman%20called%20out%20and%20the%20crowd%20tittered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20flared%20up%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20have%20us%20blessed%3F%20You%20fiend!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20portly%20Balabhadra%20babu%20owned%20a%20Xerox%2C%20scanning%20and%20printing%20shop%20in%20the%20bazaar%2C%20his%20previous%20enterprise%20in%20cyber%20cafes%20having%20failed%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20smartphones.%20Balabhadra%20babu%20was%20an%20affable%20man%3A%20early%20on%20in%20his%20printing%20career%2C%20he%20had%20landed%20a%20profitable%20contract%20for%20printing%20%E2%80%98Modi%20masks%E2%80%99%20for%20distribution%20at%20election%20rallies.%20He%20had%20made%20good%20money%20but%20even%20better%20contacts%20and%20had%20gone%20on%20to%20benefit%20greatly%20from%20that%20distinguished%20visage.%20Balabhadra%20babu%20had%20printed%20Covid%20vaccination%20certificates%2C%20posters%20felicitating%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20the%20G20%E2%80%99s%20grand%20success%2C%20and%20most%20recently%2C%20banners%20announcing%20the%20forthcoming%20inauguration%20of%20the%20grand%20temple%2C%20and%20once%20again%20commending%20the%20honourable%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20was%20usually%20clad%20in%20starched%20kurtas%20and%20pyjamas%2C%20which%20acquired%20a%20dirty%20blue%20tinge%20from%20excessive%20use%20of%20Neel%20in%20the%20wash.%20He%20was%20sipping%20tea%20at%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar%20that%20evening.%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20were%20on%20the%20opposite%20bench%2C%20talking%20softly%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20always%20carried%20an%20air%20of%20sanguinity%20about%20him.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20are%20you%20young%20people%20discussing%2C%20hain%3F%20You%20are%20young%20men%2C%20you%20should%20devote%20time%20to%20nation%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20somewhat%20superfluously%2C%20to%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmal%20had%20been%20sitting%20with%20one%20leg%20folded%20under%20him%2C%20while%20the%20other%20dangled%20off%20the%20ground.%20Excitedly%2C%20he%20unfolded%20his%20leg%20and%20stood%20up%3A%20%E2%80%9CBulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20we%20%3Cem%3Emust%3C%2Fem%3E%20work%20together.%20Our%20attitude%20should%20be%20nation%20first%3B%20everything%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20for%20minorities%20and%20backwards%20alone%2C%20while%20meritorious%20and%20nationalist%20youth%20suffer.%20We%20cannot%20allow%20this%20policy%20of%20appeasement%20any%20longer%2C%20and%20open%20cow%20slaughter%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKanwalji%20and%20Nirmalji%20suspect%20that%20Laadley%20has%20slaughtered%20a%20cow.%20They%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20catch%20them%20red-handed%2C%20but%20they%20have%20given%20him%20a%20strict%20warning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shambhu%20explained.%20Their%20status%20at%20the%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar%20had%20evidently%20changed%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20intervention.%20He%20shook%20his%20head%20resolutely%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20it%2C%20Kanwal%2C%20but%20not%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20certain%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nirmal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20here%2C%20They%20do%20it%2C%20I%20am%20aware.%20But%20not%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20about%20these%20things%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha.%20Come%20we%E2%80%99ll%20show%20you%20the%20bones%2C%20then%20you%20can%20decide%20for%20yourself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20put%20his%20half-finished%20glass%20of%20tea%20down%20and%20got%20up%20without%20a%20word.%20He%20followed%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20to%20the%20municipal%20dump%20across%20the%20street%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Shambhu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20other%20patrons%20from%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20they%20stood%20in%20a%20semi-circle%20trying%20to%20look%20for%20the%20gristle%20and%20the%20bones.%20Much%20more%20garbage%20had%20been%20piled%20on%20since%20the%20incident%20in%20the%20morning.%20Nirmal%20found%20a%20long%20stick%20and%20prodded%20the%20trash%20till%20they%20found%20the%20gristle.%20Balabhadra%20babu%20gathered%20the%20back%20of%20his%20kurta%20and%20sat%20down%20on%20his%20haunches%20to%20observe%20the%20bones%20more%20closely.%20He%20smiled%20in%20relief%20and%20shook%20his%20head%3A%20%E2%80%9DGoat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20Bulbhaddar%20chacha%2C%20look%20at%20the%20size!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9DBig%20goat%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20He%20paused%2C%20and%20then%20added%20reassuringly%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20easy%20transporting%20animals%20into%20that%20narrow%20alley.%20We%20are%20all%20here%20watching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20had%20also%20gathered%20his%20friends%20that%20evening%20for%20a%20discussion%20of%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20events.%20As%20they%20put%20out%20the%20clay%20oven%2C%20he%20had%20said%20to%20the%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%2C%20%E2%80%9CArre%20if%20we%20catch%20Jamal%20bhai%20in%20a%20good%20mood%2C%20he%20will%20lift%20your%20spirits!%20Why%20do%20you%20always%20look%20so%20sad%20and%20scared%20you%20rascal%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20lit%20himself%20a%20cigarette%2C%20took%20a%20long%20drag%20and%20coughed%3A%20%E2%80%9CThen%20Laadley%3F%20This%20has%20been%20good%20for%20your%20business%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbey%2C%20your%20little%20fight%20with%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal!%20They%20have%20declared%20that%20they%20saw%20you%20slaughter%20right%20here%20and%20everyone%20believes%20it.%20I%20heard%20someone%20say%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20go%20searching%20for%20good%20kababs%20anymore%2C%20when%20our%20Laadley%20is%20here.%20Now%20you%20can%20raise%20your%20prices%20again%20and%20continue%20to%20serve%20dog%20meat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20Khan%20touched%20his%20earlobes%20with%20the%20tip%20of%20his%20fingers%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20no%2C%20tauba%20Jamal%20bhai.%20I%E2%80%99d%20never%20do%20such%20a%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20okay.%20But%20it%20is%20true%20about%20the%20dogs%20though%2C%20what%20do%20you%20say%20Habibi%3F%20He%20peddles%20dog%20meat%20as%20mutton.%20Have%20you%20noticed%20how%20dogs%20run%20for%20cover%20when%20they%20see%20Laadley%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20seemed%20delighted%20at%20the%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20when%20there%20are%20no%20dogs%20left%2C%20he%20goes%20after%20crows.%20Have%20you%20noticed%20how%20there%20are%20no%20crows%20in%20our%20area%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20pinched%20his%20earlobes%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20all%20you%20say%20Jamal%20bhai!%20But%20by%20God%2C%20do%20you%20know%20the%20poultry%20shops%20in%20chowk%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20looked%20around%20at%20his%20audience%2C%20%E2%80%9CHain%3F%20They%20get%20these%20sickly%20local%20quails%20and%20colour%20them%20all%20neela-peela%2C%20and%20then%20sell%20them%20at%20double-price%20saying%20they%20are%20migratory%20birds%20and%20have%20only%20fed%20on%20Irani%20and%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20on%20the%20way.%20And%20people%20buy%20them%20also!%E2%80%9D%20Everyone%20burst%20into%20peals%20of%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20door%20opened%20and%20shut%20loudly%2C%20nearby%2C%20and%20Salman%20teetered%20into%20the%20alley%2C%20looking%20flushed%2C%20brushing%20his%20hair%20with%20the%20back%20of%20his%20hand.%20He%20came%20and%20sat%20on%20the%20stairs%20at%20a%20respectable%20distance%20from%20Jamal%20and%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKya%20hero%3F%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20half-witted%20husband%20is%20out%20again%20tonight%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Laadley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20blushed%20as%20the%20man%20in%20the%20checked%20lungi%20rolled%20over%20with%20laughter.%20%E2%80%9CAbey%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20fall%20into%20the%20tandoor!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%2C%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20really%20love%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20caused%20Laadley%20Khan%20to%20guffaw%20so%20much%20that%20his%20belly%20shook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20quickly%20changed%20the%20subject%3A%20%E2%80%9CLaadley%20bhai%2C%20you%20stopped%20me%2C%20otherwise%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20let%20those%20two%20get%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20did%20I%20stop%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20always%20that%20the%20police%20are%20biased.%20If%20it%20were%20just%20%3Cem%3Ethem%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20problem%2C%20but%20who%20can%20fight%20with%20the%20police%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%2C%20sheepishly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20was%20not%20biased%20today.%20Inspector%20Achche%20Lal%20contained%20the%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20both%20of%20you%20are%20finding%20fault%20with%20everything%20I%20say.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHabib%20sighed.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20everyone%20so%20angry%20all%20the%20time%3F%20First%2C%20Jamal%20bhai%20had%20a%20fight%2C%20then%20Laadley%20had%20a%20fight%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20all%20become%20radicalised%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20cackled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20foreign%20hand%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20smiled%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20Nirmal%20and%20Kanwal%20have%20had%20an%20awakening%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Eyour%3C%2Fem%3E%20Rahman%20miyan%20only%20who%20has%20encouraged%20this%20kind%20of%20activity%20in%20our%20area.%20He%20has%20brought%20the%20police%20in%20and%20now%20swine%20like%20Nirmal%20and%20Kanwal%20feel%20they%20can%20question%20us.%20Earlier%2C%20would%20anyone%20have%20dared%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20looked%20accusingly%20at%20Salman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20has%20he%20brought%20the%20police%20in%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Habib%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre!%20He%20is%20a%20daily%20informer.%20Tattles%20on%20everyone.%20Who%20said%20what%3F%20Who%20did%20what%3F%20Even%20the%20poor%20children%20in%20his%20madarsa%20%E2%80%93%20everyone%20is%20under%20scrutiny.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20spat%20dramatically.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20informed%20on%20all%20the%20anti-CAA%20protestors.%20So%20many%20had%20to%20go%20to%20jail.%20Everyone%20hates%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20Romeo%20also%20got%20into%20trouble.%20Rahman%20miyan%20has%20thrown%20him%20out%20of%20his%20quarters%20at%20the%20madarsa.%20Now%20he%20is%20forced%20to%20share%20beds%20at%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Her%20husband%20and%20our%20hero%20take%20turns%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20guffawed%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20left%20the%20madarsa%20myself.%20Rahman%20miyan%20has%20become%20too%20controlling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20coughed%20again.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20blasted%20smog.%20My%20eyes%20are%20burning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20Jamal%20bhai.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20right%20mood%20for%20murder.%20Feels%20like%20someone%20will%20die%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%20animatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChup!%20Always%20talking%20nonsense%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20growled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahrukh%20Alam%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20write%20a%20murder%20mystery%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%20She%20has%20written%20versions%20of%20this%20story%20since%202013%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%20has%20published%20one%20such%20version%20earlier.%20She%20is%20hopeful%20that%20she%E2%80%99ll%20deliver%20a%20complete%20mystery%20this%20time.%20%F0%9F%A4%9E%F0%9F%8F%BB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703565032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24075850%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-23-at-12.13.33-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-2-roti%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20WhoDunnIt%3A%20This%20is%20the%20second%20part%20of%20a%20serialised%20detective%20story%20by%20Shahrukh%20Alam.%20It%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-2-roti%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20Black%20Sea%20dominance%20'challenged'%20after%20naval%20ship%20'destroyed'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703555700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-crimea-ukraine-feodosia_6404025.jpg%3F20231226055119%22%2C%22orig