tays%20on%20forever%20and%20helps%20the%20younger%20generation%20understand%20what%20really%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20as%20an%20artist%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20experiment%20with%20new%20sounds%2C%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20our%20folk%20traditions.%20I%20tried%20to%20experiment%20with%20it%20while%20also%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20my%20grandma%20who%20recently%20told%20me%20more%20about%20these%20events%20while%20I%20was%20visiting%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FZWZo7LZA-KE%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FZWZo7LZA-KE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20standout%20feature%20of%20the%20song%20is%20the%20hook%20(chorus)%2C%20which%20Moko%20describes%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lullaby%20that%20was%20sung%20to%20us%20as%20children%20by%20our%20grandparents.%E2%80%9D%20Sung%20in%20Tenyidie%2C%20an%20indigenous%20language%20spoken%20by%20the%20Chakhesang%20Naga%20tribe%2C%20it%20brings%20a%20certain%20serenity%20amidst%20the%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20verses%20in%20the%20song%2C%20which%20are%20ver